intment%20on%20the%20climate%20front.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20disappointment%20is%20just%20as%20great%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20combating%20climate%20change.%20Despite%20the%20recent%20devastating%20succession%20of%20climate%20tragedies%2C%20the%20final%20statement%20fails%20to%20mention%20the%20objective%20of%20phasing%20out%20fossil%20fuels.%20Yet%20scientists%20consider%20this%20to%20be%20the%20only%20response%20capable%20of%20reversing%20a%20destructive%20curve%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcivil-society-calls-out-g20-declarations-omission-of-civic-space-erosion-democracy-decline%5C%22%3ECivil%20Society%20Calls%20Out%20G20%20Declaration%E2%80%99s%20Omission%20of%20Civic%20Space%20Erosion%2C%20Democracy%20Decline%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20outcome%20obviously%20reflects%20India%E2%80%99s%20rigid%20determination%20not%20to%20take%20sides%20in%20the%20war%2C%20but%20it%20is%20extraordinary%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20countries%20at%20the%20G20%20that%20do%20oppose%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20of%20conquest%20were%20so%20prepared%20to%20be%20muzzled%20by%20the%20minority%20that%20%5Bthey%5D%20prefer%20to%20look%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20UK%20official%20said%20the%20joint%20declaration%2C%20widely%20seen%20as%20weak%2C%20was%20in%20fact%20effective%20at%20putting%20pressure%20on%20Moscow.%20%E2%80%98By%20achieving%20consensus%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20G20%20has%20forced%20%5BVladimir%5D%20Putin%20to%20commit%20to%20a%20cessation%20of%20attacks%20on%20infrastructure%2C%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20troops%20and%20to%20the%20return%20of%20territory%2C%E2%80%99%20they%20said.%E2%80%9D%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2Fsep%2F10%2Fwatered-down-g20-statement-on-ukraine-is-sign-of-indias-growing-influence%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Csp