%20end%20of%20the%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20prepared%20my%20game%20in%20a%20way%20I%20can%20help%20the%20team.%20Today%20was%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20you%20don't%20get%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start...%20KL%20started%20better%2C%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20bring%20him%20on%20strike%20and%20playing%20second%20fiddle%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kohli%20when%20asked%20about%20his%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20yes%2C%20then%20after%20that%20I%20stepped%20up%20where%20I%20could.%20I%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20pride%20in%20fitness.%20Pushing%20for%20doubles%20are%20easy%20runs%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20big%20shot.%20It%20has%20paid%20off%20before%2C%20hope%20to%20continue%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20partnership%20with%20Rahul%2C%20Kohli%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BBoth%20KL%20and%20myself%20are%20both%20conventional%20players.%20And%20when%20you%20have%20him%20batting%20the%20way%20he%20was%20and%20me%20playing%2C%20its%20tough%20to%20break%20these%20partnerships%20because%20we%20don't%20play%20fancy%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20think%20about%20the%20partnership%20too%20much%2C%20the%20idea%20was%20to%20'keep%20batting.'%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20memorable%20partnerships%20we've%20had%20and%20for%20Indian%20cricket%20as%20well.%20He%20hit%20form%20for%20us%20straightaway%2C%20good%20for%20us%20(going%20into%20the%20World%20Cup).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20rain%2C%20India%20will%20end%20up%20playing%20three%20days%20in%20a%20row%20as%20they%20take%20on%20Sri%20Lanka%20here%20on%20Tuesday.%20They%20romped%20to%20a%20228%20run%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20on%20the%20reserve%20day%20after%20only%2024.1%20overs%20were%20possible%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20was%20understandably%20tired%20after%20an%20epic%20knock%20but%20come%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20will%20be%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20first%20time%20I%20have%20done%20anything%20(play%20back-to-back%20ODIs)%20like%20this%20in%2015%20years%20of%20cricket.%20Luckily%2C%20we%20are%20Test%20players%2C%20so%20we%20know%20how%20to%20come%20back%20the%20next%20day%20and%20play.%20Recovery%20is%20crucial.%20It%20was%20humid%20out%20there%20today.%20I%20will%20be%2035%20in%20November%2C%20so%20I%20need%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20big%20shout-out%20to%20the%20groundstaff%20from%20my%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20when%20asked%20about%20taking%20the%20field%20in%20less%20than%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694517720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fdcaivno8_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_12_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2F38-singles-and-15-twos-virat-kohli-takes-pride-in-fitness-on-way-to-century-against-pakistan-4381294%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20took%2038%20singles%20and%20ran%2015%20doubles%20as%20he%20scored%20a%20century%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20Super%204%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2F38-singles-and-15-twos-virat-kohli-takes-pride-in-fitness-on-way-to-century-against-pakistan-4381294%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2F38-singles-and-15-twos-virat-kohli-takes-pride-in-fitness-on-way-to-century-against-pakistan-4381294%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2F38-singles-and-15-twos-virat-kohli-takes-pride-in-fitness-on-way-to-century-against-pakistan-4381294%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22American%20researcher%20doing%20well%20after%2