llegedly%20Attacking%20BJP%20Leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160828%2FThe-Wire-6.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Police%20has%20lodged%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20former%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%20(DGP)%20Jagmohan%20Yadav%20for%20allegedly%20assaulting%20and%20threatening%20a%20block-level%20office%20bearer%20of%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20Jaunpur%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20retired%20in%202015.%20He%20served%20as%20the%20DGP%20under%20the%20previous%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20under%20chief%20minister%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20from%20July%202015%20to%20December%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20was%20lodged%20against%20Yadav%20at%20Mungra%20Badshahpur%20police%20station%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20Chandresh%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20a%20village%20headman%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20local%20mandal%20adhyaksh.%20Yadav%2C%20a%201983-batch%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%2C%20was%20booked%20under%20Sections%20323%20(voluntarily%20causing%20hurt)%2C%20504%20(intentional%20insult%20with%20intent%20to%20provoke%20breach%20of%20peace)%2C%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircle%20officer%20Machhlishahr%2C%20Atar%20Singh%2C%20said%20as%20per%20the%20complaint%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20when%20officials%20of%20the%20revenue%20team%20and%20chakbandi%20department%20had%20gathered%20in%20the%20secretariat%20of%20the%20gram%20sabha%20Tarahati%20on%20Monday%20afternoon%20to%20settle%20land%20disputes%20and%20grievances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETarahati%20is%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20native%20village%20where%20his%20mother%20served%20as%20a%20former%20gram%20pradhan%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20September%2011%2C%20when%20local%20villagers%20led%20by%20headman%20Gupta%20were%20raising%20their%20grievances%20with%20revenue%20officials%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Etehsildar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Elekhpal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20local%20SHO%2C%20and%20others%2C%20Yadav%20barged%20into%20the%20hall%2C%20alleged%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20when%20he%20saw%20Yadav%20he%20got%20up%20from%20his%20chair%20as%20a%20mark%20of%20respect%20but%20Yadav%20insulted%20him%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20hall%20after%20knowing%20his%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20got%20all%20fired%20up%2C%20grabbed%20my%20collar%20and%20struck%20me%20twice%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20leave%20the%20panchayat%20bhavan%2C%E2%80%9D%20alleged%20Gupta%20in%20his%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Gupta%20accused%20Yadav%20and%20his%20family%20of%20illegally%20grabbing%20village%20land%2C%20including%20the%20land%20of%20the%20gram%20sabha%2C%20land%20of%20a%20local%20girls%E2%80%99%20school%20and%20barren%20patches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20had%20illegally%20grabbed%20a%20lot%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village%20and%20the%20villagers%20were%20in%20the%20panchayat%20bhavan%20to%20raise%20their%20complaints%20when%20Yadav%20showed%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20he%20had%20any%20personal%20enmity%20or%20dispute%20with%20Yadav%2C%20Gupta%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20only%20met%20him%20once%20before%20this%2C%20when%20his%20brother%20had%20expired.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECircle%20officer%20Singh%20said%20the%20matter%20was%20being%20probed.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20with%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694517336000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160828%2FThe-Wire-6.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-registers-fir-against-ex-dgp-jagmohan-yadav-for-allegedly-attacking-bjp-leader%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yadav%20served%20as%20the%20DGP%20under%20the%20previous%20Samajwadi%20Party%20government%20headed%20by%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20from%20July%20to%20December%202015.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fup-police-registers-fir-against-ex-dgp-jagmohan-yadav-for-allegedly-attacking-bjp-leader%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Govt's%20Statement%20Against%20Security%20Forces%20Goes%20Against%20Its%20Own%20Police's%20Version%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07091212%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-9.10.56.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fsequence-of-events-shows-disconnect-between-biren-singh-government-and-forces%2Fcid%2F1965528%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20highlighted%20the%20deepening%20mistrust%20between%20the%20Manipur%20state%20government%20and%20the%20central%20forces%20who%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20the%20state%20to%20tackle%20the%20nearly%20four-month-long%20ethnic%20violence%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20an%20incident%20on%20September%208%20of%20gunfighting%20between%20an%20armed%20group%20identified%20as%20comprising%20Meitei%20community%20members%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20in%20a%20Kuki-majority%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Meitei%20mob%2C%20informed%20of%20this%20fight%2C%20gathered%20at%20Pallel%20in%20Tengnoupal%20district%20with%20the%20view%20of%20travelling%20to%20the%20village%20to%20support%20the%20armed%20group%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mob%20shot%20at%20security%20forces%2C%20who%20allegedly%20retaliated%2C%20sources%20told%20the%20paper.%20Three%20civilians%20were%20killed%20and%20several%2C%20including%20an%20army%20officer%2C%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20day%20later%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20cabinet%20had%20%E2%80%9Ccondemned%20the%20unwanted%20actions%20of%20the%20central%20security%20forces%E2%80%9D%20on%20civilians%20the%20previous%20day%20at%20Pallel%20and%20noted%20that%20it%20would%20apprise%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20the%20cabinet%E2%80%99s%20statement%20contradicts%20the%20state%20police%E2%80%99s%20own%20media%20statement%20on%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20calibrated%20response%20in%20self-defence%20and%20to%20control%20the%20unruly%20mob%2C%20security%20forces%20used%20minimum%20force%20to%20disperse%20the%20mob%20that%20led%20to%20injuries%20to%20a%20few%20persons%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20mob%20out%20of%20which%20two%20reportedly%20died.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20noted%20that%20the%20firing%20had%20been%20against%20%E2%80%9Carmed%20miscreants%20who%20attempted%20to%20resort%20to%20arson%20and%20violence%20in%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20statement%20highlighted%20that%20cops%20were%20working%20closely%20with%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cjoint%20operation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYet%2C%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20statement%20of%20condemnation%20mentioned%20only%20central%20security%20forces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20the%20state%20home%20ministry%2C%20held%20by%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20contains%20details%20gleaned%20from%20sources%20who%20said%20that%20security%20personnel%20had%20resorted%20to%20firing%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20exhausting%20all%20options%20to%20break%20up%20the%20huge%20crowd%2C%20including%20requests%20to%20them%20to%20disperse%20followed%20by%20a%20baton-charge%2C%20tear%20gas%20shelling%2C%20the%20firing%20of%20rubber%20bullets%2C%20and%20then%20the%20firing%20of%20bullets%20below%20the%20waist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20growing%20division%20between%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20the%20security%20forces%20deployed%20to%20ensure%20calm%20in%20the%20state%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmanipur-violence-imphal-media-army-letter-editors-guild%5C%22%3Ereflected%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Army%20wrote%20to%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20local%20media%20supporting%20one%20community%20over%20the%20other%2C%20and%20worsening%20the%20strife%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20letter%2C%20publicised%20a%20day%20ago%2C%20assumes%20significance%20as%20the%20Editors%20Guild%20is%C2%A0facing%20a%20first%20information%20report%20filed%20by%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20against%20it%20over%20a%20fact-finding%20report%20it%20released%20on%20the%20news%20environment%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694517302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-violence-security-forces-army-police-cabinet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'Telegraph'%20report%20notes%20how%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20and%20Manipur%20Police%20have%20differing%20versions%20of%20gunfight%20between%20an%20armed%20group%20and%20the%20security%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple's%20iPhone%2015%20Launch%20Clouded%20By%20China%20Problems%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20expected%20to%20unveil%20a%20new%20iPhone%2015%20lineup%20as%20questions%20about%20market%20access%20in%20China%20and%20competition%20hang%20over%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20listed%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%20made%20up%20more%20than%20half%20of%20Apple's%20%24394.3%20billion%20in%20sales%20last%20year%2C%20but%20it%20faces%20new%20challenges%20with%20selling%20in%20China%2C%20the%20Cupertino%2C%20California%20firm's%20third-largest%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20latest%20phones%20are%20expected%20to%20have%20new%20charging%20ports%2C%20titanium%20cases%2C%20and%20cameras%2C%20but%20their%20debut%20at%20its%20Apple%20Park%20headquarters%20at%2010%20am%20PT%20(1700%20GMT)%20will%20come%20as%20the%20Chinese%20government%20has%20expanded%20some%20restrictions%20on%20using%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20will%20also%20have%20to%20grapple%20with%20competition%20from%20Huawei%20Technologies%2C%20which%20was%20its%20top%20rival%20in%20China's%20premium%20smartphone%20market%20until%20US%20export%20controls%20ruined%20Huawei's%20phone%20business%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Huawei%20started%20selling%20the%20Mate%2060%20Pro%2C%20a%20high-end%20phone%20that%20uses%20Chinese-made%20chips%20that%20some%20US%20lawmakers%20believe%20were%20manufactured%20in%20violation%20of%20US%20trade%20curbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHuawei%20wants%20to%20gain%20an%20edge%20over%20Apple%20with%20add-on%20features%20like%20satellite%20calling%20that%20relies%20on%20China's%20government-backed%20network.%20Apple's%20current%20iPhone%20lineup%20includes%20satellite%20capabilities%2C%20though%20they%20are%20meant%20only%20for%20emergency%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20iphone%2015%20Launch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20likely%20to%20focus%20on%20its%20new%20product%20lineup.%20By%20far%20the%20biggest%20change%20for%20most%20Apple%20customers%20will%20be%20a%20switch%20from%20Apple's%20propriety%20%26quot%3BLightning%26quot%3B%20charging%20cables%20to%20USB-C%2C%20a%20standard%20that%20Apple%20already%20uses%20on%20its%20laptops%20and%20some%20high-end%20iPads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20was%20forced%20into%20the%20change%20by%20European%20regulations%2C%20but%20analysts%20believe%20that%20the%20company%20will%20position%20the%20change%20as%20an%20upgrade%2C%20taking%20advantage%20of%20faster%20data%20speeds%20that%20can%20transfer%20high-quality%20videos%20made%20with%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20are%20also%20expecting%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bperiscope%26quot%3B%20camera%20technology%20that%20could%20give%20phones%20better%20zoom%20capabilities%20and%20titanium%20cases%2C%20as%20well%20as%20upgraded%20chips.%20Such%20%26quot%3Bperiscope%26quot%3B%20lenses%20can%20use%20mirrors%20or%20prisms%20to%20get%20a%20longer%20lens%20without%20having%20to%20make%20the%20camera%20module%20much%20larger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20question%20of%20the%20day%20will%20be%20whether%20Apple%20reserves%20those%20features%20for%20a%20new%20top-end%20device%20and%20makes%20smaller%20upgrades%20to%20its%20cheaper%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20like%20we%20saw%20people%20who%20aren't%20Ultra%20athletes%20buy%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20Ultra%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20see%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20buy%20this%20even%20if%20they%20aren't%20camera%20or%20photography%20enthusiasts%2C%20just%20because%20they%20like%20the%20latest%20and%20greatest%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ben%20Bajarin%2C%20chief%20executive%20and%20principal%20analyst%20of%20Creative%20Strategies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20by%20itself%20creates%20that%20buzz%20and%20momentum%20and%20allure%20to%20the%20top%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EApple%20To%20Increase%20Avg%20Price%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20expected%20to%20increase%20the%20average%20price%20per%20phone%20sold%20to%20boost%20its%20revenue%2C%20but%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20it%20does%20that%20by%20raising%20prices%20across%20the%20board%20or%20just%20on%20premium%20versions.%20The%20global%20smartphone%20market%20has%20slumped%20from%20shipping%20294.5%20million%20total%20phones%20to%20268%20million%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%2C%20but%20Apple's%20shipments%20declined%20the%20least%20of%20any%20major%20smartphone%20maker%2C%20dropping%20from%2046.5%20million%20phones%20to%2045.3%20million%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Counterpoint%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%20is%2C%20we're%20in%20a%20very%20down%20smartphone%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bob%20O'Donnell%2C%20head%20of%20TECHnalysis%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Donnell%20said%20he%20will%20also%20be%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20any%20hints%20about%20Apple's%20plans%20with%20what%20is%20known%20as%20generative%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20the%20technology%20trend%20behind%20applications%20like%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20and%20Microsoft's%20%26quot%3BCopilot%26quot%3B%20assistant%20technologies%20for%20its%20Office%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20have%20repeatedly%20prodded%20Apple%20about%20its%20plans%20for%20such%20technology%20but%20the%20company%20has%20given%20few%20hints%20so%20far%2C%20other%20than%20Chief%20Executive%20Tim%20Cook's%20comments%20in%20July%20that%20the%20company's%20secret%20work%20on%20the%20technology%20is%20driving%20up%20its%20research%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWill%20Apple%20tease%20an%20advanced%20form%20of%20Siri%3F%20That%20would%20be%20something%20that%20would%20generate%20some%20excitement%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Donnell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694517000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F2seubkt8_apple-iphone_625x300_12_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fapples-iphone-15-launch-clouded-by-china-problems-4382606%