uanced%20scholarship%2C%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20seems%20to%20have%20created%20a%20symbol%20emptied%20out%20of%20its%20historical%2C%20political%20and%20ethical%20content%20but%20naturalised%20through%20propagandist%20rituals%20repeated%20inexorably.%20Govind%20Krishnan%20V.%20is%20trying%20to%20evaluate%20this%20claim%20of%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20in%20his%20recently%20published%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EVivekananda%2C%20the%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Epublished%20by%20Aleph%20Books.%20Govind%E2%80%99s%20task%20becomes%20particularly%20daunting%20because%20a%20body%20of%20recent%20scholarship%2C%20coming%20from%20parts%20of%20the%20left%20and%20the%20marginalised%2C%20echo%20the%20Hindutva%20views%20on%20the%20man.%20Given%20the%20available%20narratives%2C%20Govind%20tries%20to%20create%20a%20third%20narrative%20to%20establish%20how%20Vivekananda%20is%20not%20just%20outside%20inclusive%2C%20egalitarian%20political%20thought%20and%20social%20action%20but%20should%20be%20a%20beacon%20of%20it.%20The%20book%E2%80%99s%20reiteration%20on%20the%20anti-Sangh%20nature%20of%20Vivekananda%20becomes%20an%20act%20in%20reclaiming%20his%20legacy%2C%20almost%20making%20it%20one%20to%20inherit%2C%20reminding%20us%20of%20Walter%20Benjamin%E2%80%99s%20observation%20in%20%3Cem%3EOn%20the%20Concept%20of%20History%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20historian%20capable%20of%20fanning%20the%20spark%20of%20hope%20in%20the%20past%20is%20the%20one%20who%20is%20firmly%20convinced%20that%20even%20the%20dead%20will%20not%20be%20safe%20from%20the%20enemy%20if%20he%20is%20victorious.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%E2%80%99s%20methodology%20is%20quite%20effective%3A%20he%20outlines%20the%20political%20events%20and%20developments%20of%20our%20times%20and%20elaborates%20on%20the%20positions%20of%20Hindutva%20leaders%20that%20forms%20the%20ideological%20base%20for%20these.%20Then%20he%20brings%20out%20the%20underlying%20political%20philosophy%2C%20explaining%20the%20position%20of%20Vivekananda%2C%20both%20through%20analysis%20and%20presentation%20of%20historical%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20279px)%2085vw%2C%20279px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160655%2F71B4qoHMXmL._AC_UF350350_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22279%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160655%2F71B4qoHMXmL._AC_UF350350_QL80_.jpg%20237w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12160655%2F71B4qoHMXmL._AC_UF350350_QL80_-203x300.jpg%20203w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672718%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22412%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGovind%20Krishnan%20V.%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EVivekananda%2C%20the%20Philosopher%20of%20Freedom%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EAleph%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20identifies%20the%20first%20contradiction%20between%20Vivekananda%20and%20Hindutva%20outlook%20in%20that%20the%20latter%20blames%20outsiders%2C%20be%20that%20the%20rule%20by%20Muslim%20kings%20or%20that%20of%20the%20British%20empire%20(dubbed%20Christian%20by%20the%20Hindu%20right).%20Vivekananda%20held%20that%20the%20downfall%20was%20due%20to%20the%20dominant%20castes%20of%20India%3A%20%E2%80%9COur%20aristocratic%20ancestors%20went%20on%20treading%20the%20common%20masses%20of%20our%20country%20underfoot%2C%20till%20they%20became%20helpless%2C%20till%20under%20this%20torment%20the%20poor%2C%20poor%20people%20nearly%20forgot%20that%20they%20were%20human%20beings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20Hindus%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20Shivaganga%2C%20during%20a%20welcome%20meeting%20after%20the%20American%20journey%2C%20Vivekananda%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20neither%20Vedandists%2C%20most%20of%20us%20now%2C%20nor%20Pauranikas%2C%20nor%20Tantrikas%2C%20we%20are%20just%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20Touchists%E2%80%99.%20Our%20religion%20is%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Our%20God%20is%20the%20Cooking-pot%20and%20our%20religion%20is%2C%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99t%20touch%20me.%20I%20am%20holy%E2%80%99.%20If%20this%20goes%20on%20for%20another%20century%20every%20one%20of%20us%20will%20be%20in%20the%20lunatic%20asylum.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivekananda%20held%20not%20Hindu%20religion%20but%20Hindu%20society%20guilty%20for%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20exploitation.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20religion%20on%20earth%20preaches%20the%20dignity%20of%20humanity%20in%20such%20a%20lofty%20strain%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20and%20no%20religion%20on%20earth%20treads%20upon%20the%20necks%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20low%20in%20such%20a%20fashion%20as%20Hinduism.%E2%80%9D%20While%20Hindutva%20tries%20to%20consolidate%20power%20through%20manufactured%20and%20perceived%20fears%20and%20insecurities%20about%20the%20outsider%20expressed%20through%20symbols%20of%20power%2C%20Vivekananda%20is%20looking%20inwards%2C%20at%20concrete%20social%20situations%20and%20historical%20realities%2C%20with%20enormous%20ethical%20courage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outsider-villain%20is%20furthered%20through%20%E2%80%9Cforeign%20religions%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Sangh%20narrative%20and%20Vivekananda%20not%20only%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20share%20the%20Hindu%20supremacist%20position%20but%20he%20actively%20opposes%20the%20parochial%20view.%20One%20of%20the%20two%20books%2C%20points%20out%20Govind%2C%20Vivekananda%20carried%20in%20his%20travels%20is%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Imitation%20of%20Christ%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20book%20on%20Christian%20mysticism%2C%20authored%20by%20Thomas%20a%20Kempis%20%E2%80%93%20he%20also%20later%20translated%20this%20book%20to%20Bengali%20with%20the%20title%20%3Cem%3EIshanusarana%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20also%20brought%20to%20our%20notice%20that%20%E2%80%9CIn%20America%2C%20many%20of%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20lectures%20were%20held%20in%20Unitarian%20churches%E2%80%9D.%20Constance%20Towne%E2%80%99s%20account%20of%20a%20church%20visit%20demonstrates%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20best%3A%20%E2%80%9CHe%20went%20to%20mass%20with%20me%20at%20St.%20Leo%E2%80%99s%20Church%2C%20the%20little%20one%20on%20Twenty-eight%20Street%E2%80%A6There%20he%20knelt%20at%20the%20high%20noon%20at%20the%20canon%20of%20the%20Mass.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Remembering%209%2F11%20Speech%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20That%20Warned%20Us%20of%20the%20Dangers%20Posed%20by%20Fanaticism%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fremembering-9-11-speech-of-swami-vivekananda-that-warned-us-of-the-dangers-posed-by-fanaticism%5C%22%3ERemembering%209%2F11%20Speech%20of%20Swami%20Vivekananda%20That%20Warned%20Us%20of%20the%20Dangers%20Posed%20by%20Fanaticism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20narrates%20instances%20where%20Vivekananda%20defended%20the%20egalitarian%20outlook%20and%20universal%20fellow-feeling%20that%20Islam%20preached%20when%20Western%20Christians%20and%20missionaries%20tried%20to%20dismiss%20Islam%20as%20crazy%20and%20archaic.%20His%20appreciation%20for%20Mughal%20architecture%20and%20aesthetic%20surely%20reads%20as%20an%20antidote%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20project%2C%20which%20understands%20history%20as%20gravedigging%20of%20the%20present.%20In%20Christine%20Greenfield%E2%80%99s%20words%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Moghuls%20seemed%20to%20have%20cast%20a%20spell%20over%20Swami%20Vivekananda%2F%20He%20depicted%20this%20period%20of%20Indian%20history%20with%20such%20dramatic%20intensity%2C%20that%20the%20idea%20often%20came%20to%20us%20that%20he%20was%20telling%20the%20story%20of%20his%20own%20past.%E2%80%9D%20Govind%20maps%20the%20Muslim%20presences%20in%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20journey%20including%20Muslims%20whose%20hospitality%20he%20accepted%2C%20quite%20contrary%20to%20the%20prevailing%20norms.%20His%20response%20when%20questioned%20on%20staying%20and%20eating%20at%20a%20Muslim%20household%20is%20revealing%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20God%2C%20for%20he%20sanctions%20it.%20I%20am%20not%20afraid%20of%20the%20scriptures%20for%20they%20allow%20it%3A%20but%20I%20am%20afraid%20of%20you%20people%20and%20your%20society.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20situates%20Vivekananda%20in%20two%20traditions%3A%20one%2C%20in%20the%20Indic%20spiritual%20tradition%20as%20a%20practical%20vedanist%2C%20with%20a%20key%20social%20sense%20on%20hunger%20and%20backward%20suffering.%20Second%2C%20in%20the%20Victorian%20period%20as%20a%20person%20who%20is%20trying%20to%20creating%20an%20enabling%20theoretical%20perspective%2C%20using%20British%20empiricism%20and%20German%20idealism%20with%20a%20Romantic%20aesthetic.%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20individual%20freedom%20(%E2%80%9CLet%20men%20have%20liberty.%20That%20is%20the%20only%20condition%20for%20growth%E2%80%9D)%2C%20Govind%20substantiates%2C%20goes%20completely%20against%20a%20supremacist%20ideology%20and%20organisational%20set%20up%20of%20Hindutva%20organisations%20that%20seek%20complete%20submission%20of%20the%20individual.%20Govind%20historicises%20Vivekananda%20enough%20for%20the%20modern%20reader%2C%20by%20providing%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20number%20of%20his%20positions%20that%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20jar!%20The%20intellectual%20honesty%20with%20which%20such%20instances%20have%20been%20identified%20and%20presented%20is%20noteworthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGovind%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20at%20all%20engage%20with%20the%20academically%20powerful%20post-colonial%20school%20of%20thought%20and%20its%20readings%20of%20Vivekananda%2C%20even%20as%20an%20exploration%20of%20the%20absence%20%E2%80%93%20in%20that%20the%20book%20is%20courageously%20unfashionable.%20The%20situating%20of%20Vivekananda%20in%20medieval%20Indian%20traditions%20remains%20half-hearted.%20In%20his%20insightful%20and%20nuanced%20comparing%20and%20contrasting%20of%20Vivekananda%20and%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20author%20does%20point%20to%20the%20theoretical%20possibility%20of%20capturing%20the%20visions%20of%20justice%20and%20equality%20%E2%80%93%20an%20idea%20to%20be%20furthered%20using%20Gandhian%20ethics%20and%20praxis%20%E2%80%93%20a%20link%20the%20book%20curiously%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20develop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reading%20this%20book%2C%20one%20gets%20the%20sense%20of%20an%20amazingly%20free%20personality%20%E2%80%93%20one%20who%20cherished%20and%20upheld%20his%20religion%20and%20culture%20but%20with%20confidence%2C%20resourcefulness%2C%20grace%2C%20rigour%20and%20even%20wit.%20Vivekananda%20comes%20across%20as%20both%20a%20critical%20insider%20and%20a%20powerful%20spokesperson%20of%20Hindu%20religious%20thought%20in%20Govind%E2%80%99s%20articulation.%20The%20dyanamicity%20of%20an%20evolving%2C%20concrete%20world%20and%20guidance%20received%20for%20it%20from%20the%20abstract%2C%20ethical%20principles%20pushes%20him%2C%20perhaps%2C%20towards%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20universal%20religion.%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20views%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20(%E2%80%9Cthe%20best%20thermometer%20to%20the%20progress%20of%20a%20nation%20is%20its%20treatment%20of%20women%E2%80%9D)%2C%20much%20advanced%20for%20his%20age%2C%20shows%20the%20possibilities%20of%20freedom%20and%20the%20need%20to%20universalise%20it.%20This%20engagement%20with%20a%20changing%20world%20also%20counters%20the%20revivalist%20impulse%20of%20the%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20scheme.%20Reading%20about%20this%20Vivekananda%20is%20a%20heartily%20enabling%20process%2C%20one%20that%20makes%20hope%20possible%20and%20not%20despair%20convincing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vivekananda%20Dismissed%20Hindutva%20View%20That%20Blames%20Foreign%20Invasions%20for%20India's%20Civilisational%20Decline%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fvivekananda-dismissed-hindutva-view-that-blames-foreign-invasions-for-indias-civilisational-decline%5C%22%3EVivekananda%20Dismissed%20Hindutva%2