0not%20at%20all%20worth%20the%20scrutiny%2C%20negativity%20(let's%20be%20honest)%2C%20or%20integrity%20risks%20that%20come%20along%20with%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20has%20been%20gradually%20pivoting%20away%20from%20news%20across%20its%20various%20platforms%2C%20as%20social%20media%20sites%20such%20as%20Facebook%20have%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20for%20spreading%20misinformation%20and%20political%20division.%20Both%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2021%2Fnov%2F02%2Ffacebook-failing-to-protect-users-from-covid-misinformation-says-monitor%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freport-facebook-tech-is-failing-to-detect-vaccine-misinformation-2021-10%5C%22%3Efailing%20to%20protect%20users%20from%20COVID-19%20misinformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20pandemic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-instragram-threads-blocks-searches-about-covid-political-news-19-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694515096000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6500325ddb12d3001906415c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-instragram-threads-blocks-searches-about-covid-political-news-19-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20has%20temporarily%20blocked%20searches%20for%20COVID-19-related%20topics%20on%20Threads%20after%20rolling%20out%20a%20new%20search%20tool%20for%20its%20X%20rival.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tcarter%40insider.com%20(Tom%20Carter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-instragram-threads-blocks-searches-about-covid-political-news-19-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%2C000%20Missing%20After%20Deadly%20Floods%20In%20Easte