ast%20month%2C%20has%20now%20become%20a%20household%20name%2C%20with%20the%20agitation%20taking%20an%20aggressive%20turn%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20three-decade-old%20demand%2C%20now%20revived%20by%20Jarange-Patil%2C%20went%20out%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20control%20with%20sporadic%20%3Cem%3Ebandhs%3C%2Fem%3E%20being%20announced%20across%20many%20districts.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20agitation%20turned%20violent%20with%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesters%2C%20further%20worsening%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20assembly%20elections%20in%20sight%2C%20the%20vexed%20problem%20of%20Maratha%20reservation%20demand%20is%20once%20again%20back%20to%20dominate%20the%20state%20politics.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20weeks%2C%20political%20leaders%20across%20parties%20have%20been%20making%20a%20beeline%20to%20meet%20Jarange-Patil%20and%20extend%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJarange-Patil%2C%20who%20has%20been%20active%20in%20Maratha%20politics%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20says%20he%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Capolitical%20person%E2%80%9D%2C%20working%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20his%20community.%20At%20the%20start%20of%20his%20career%2C%20he%20was%20active%20with%20a%20Maratha%20organisation%20headed%20by%20Purushottam%20Khedekar.%20He%20later%20started%20his%20own%20organisation%2C%20%E2%80%98Shivba%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20demands%20of%20this%20agitation%20is%20the%20issuance%20of%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community.%20The%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20on%20September%207%2C%20issued%20a%20resolution%20saying%20that%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20all%20Marathas%20from%20the%20Marathwada%20region%20who%20possess%20the%20%E2%80%98Nizam-era%E2%80%99%20documents%20such%20as%20revenue%2C%20educational%20and%20other%20supporting%20records%2C%20and%20if%20%E2%80%9CKunbi%E2%80%9D%20is%20mentioned%20in%20their%20genealogy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20resolution%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20Jarange-Patil%20and%20his%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20protest%2C%20Jarange-Patil%20has%20maintained%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20the%20agitation%20until%20his%20demands%20are%20fully%20met.%20But%20he%20is%20willing%20to%20have%20a%20dialogue%20with%20the%20government.%20The%20government%20had%20called%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Call-party%E2%80%9D%20meeting%20where%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20the%20home%20department%20would%20withdraw%20all%20the%20cases%20against%20the%20protesters%20in%20the%20Jalna%20district%20where%20the%20police%20had%20resorted%20to%20lathicharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Shinde%2C%20addressing%20the%20media%20late%20Monday%20evening%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20requested%20him%20%5BJarange-Patil%5D%20to%20give%20time%20to%20the%20Justice%20Shinde%20committee%20to%20set%20up%20(a%20proposal%20on%20the%20viability%20of%20giving%20Kunbi%20certificates%20to%20Marathas).%20We%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20include%20him%20or%20his%20representative%20in%20the%20committee.%20We%20have%20also%20agreed%20to%20suspend%20three%20officials%20responsible%20for%20the%20lathicharge%2C%20expressing%20apology%20over%20the%20lathicharge%20incident.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%2C%20who%20leads%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20is%20a%20Maratha%20leader.%20His%20deputy%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20is%20also%20from%20the%20dominant%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%2C%20estimated%20(although%20never%20enumerated)%20to%20constitute%20over%2033%25%20of%20the%20state%20population%2C%20enjoys%20political%20dominance%20in%20the%20state.%20A%20land-owning%20community%2C%20Marathas%20hold%20control%20over%20most%20sugar%20cooperatives%20in%20the%20state.%20Many%20privately%20run%20educational%20institutions%20belong%20to%20the%20community%20leaders.%20Since%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20Maharashtra%20state%20in%201960%2C%2012%20out%20of%2020%20chief%20ministers%20belonged%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20privileges%2C%20the%20community%20leaders%20say%2C%20have%20been%20enjoyed%20only%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20families.%20The%20community%2C%20as%20claimed%20by%20the%20agitators%2C%20continues%20to%20be%20marginalised%20by%20and%20large%20and%20has%20therefore%20been%20demanding%20reservation%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20has%20had%20a%20long%20tradition%20of%20anti-Brahmin%20movements%2C%20led%20by%20Maratha%20stalwarts%20like%20Keshavrao%20Jedhe%20and%20Dinkarrao%20Jawalkar.%20The%20community%20is%20known%20for%20its%20violent%20and%20dominant%20caste%20pride.%20In%20the%20Maratha-majority%20villages%2C%20the%20caste-atrocities%20inflicted%20by%20the%20Marathas%20on%20the%20Dalit%20community%20is%20very%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservation%20is%20not%20new%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%2032%20years%20ago%2C%20Mathadi%20Labour%20Union%20leader%20Annasaheb%20Patil%20first%20began%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20agitation.%20The%20demand%20has%20time%20and%20again%20come%20up%2C%20mostly%20around%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20just%20months%20before%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20then%20state%20chief%20minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%2C%20relying%20on%20the%20then%20Narayan%20Rane%20committee%20report%2C%20brought%20in%20an%20ordinance%20introducing%2016%25%20reservation%20for%20the%20community%2C%20particularly%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20taken%20forward%20by%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis-led%20government%20in%202014.%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-maratha-reservation-pleas-maharashtra%5C%22%3Ebrought%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%2016%25%20reservation%20down%20to%2013%25%20in%20jobs%20and%2012%25%20in%20education.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20quashed%20the%20quota%20altogether%20for%20Marathas.%20%E2%80%9CReservation%20cannot%20cross%20the%2050%25%20limit%20in%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmaratha-quota-case-sc-declares-reservation-over-50-as-unconstitutional%5C%22%3Ethe%20court%20opined.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20trying%20hard%20to%20defuse%20the%20situation%20that%20Jarange-Patil%E2%80%99s%20agitation%20has%20led%20in%20the%20state.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20state%20has%20offered%20only%20a%20partial%20solution.%20Allowing%20the%20Maratha%20community%20into%20the%20OBC%20fold%20would%20mean%20eating%20up%20into%20the%20already%20limited%20pool.%20Many%20OBC%20communities%2C%20especially%20the%20Kunbi%20community%2C%20are%20already%20up%20in%20arms%20and%20are%20pushing%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20outfits%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kunbi%2C%20Mali%20and%20Dhangar%20communities%20have%20initiated%20protests%20across%20the%20state%20against%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move%20to%20integrate%20Marathas%20as%20Kunbis%20in%20the%20OBC%20quota.%20While%20the%20state%20government%20is%20busy%20initiating%20dialogues%20with%20Jarange-Patil%20and%20other%20Maratha%20leaders%2C%20the%20OBCs%20say%20the%20government%20has%20completely%20ignored%20them.%20The%20leaders%20have%20decided%20to%20stage%20an%20indefinite%20sit-in%20protest%20beginning%20Sunday%20(September%2017)%20until%20the%20government%20assures%20them%20that%20it%20will%20not%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20community%20has%20long%20been%20divided%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20Maratha%20and%20Kunbis%20as%20one.%20A%20meeting%20of%20the%20larger%20OBC%20community%20was%20recently%20organised%20in%20Nagpur.%20The%20OBC%20Mahasangh%20president%2C%20Baban%20Taywade%2C%20who%20attended%20the%20meeting%2C%20appealed%20to%20the%20OBC%20community%20to%20en%20masse%20oppose%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Marathas%20are%20a%20separate%20community%20and%20cannot%20be%20incorporated%20as%20a%20sub-caste%20in%20the%20OBC.%20The%20Marathas%20have%20been%20demanding%20reservation%20and%20we%20are%20not%20opposed%20to%20it.%20But%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20simply%20be%20bunched%20along%20with%20us.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20this%20under%20pressure%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20oppose%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Taywade%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694514601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F24182632%2Fmaratha-kH1E-621x414%2540LiveMint.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20primary%20demands%20of%20this%20agitation%20is%20the%20issuance%20of%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20for%20all%20members%20of%20the%20Maratha%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fan%20'attacked%20and%20gang%20raped'%20in%20France%20during%20Rugby%20World%20Cup%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694514060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-france-bordeaux-police_6282107.jpg%3F20230912110818%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fireland-fan-allegedly-gang-raped-in-france-during-rugby-world-cup-opening-weekend-12959643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Ireland%20fan%20was%20allegedly%20gang%20raped%20in%20Bordeaux%20during%20the%20opening%20weekend%20of%20the%20Rugby%20World%20Cup%2C%20according%20to%20reports%20in%20French%20media.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fn