ngeles%20Times%20via%20Getty%20Images%3B%20CHRIS%20DELMAS%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETaylor%20Swift's%20Eras%20Tour%20movie%20was%20approved%20for%20an%20interim%20agreement%20through%20SAG-AFTRA.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESAG-AFTRA%20represents%20actors%2C%20and%20its%20over%20160%2C000%20members%20are%20currently%20on%20strike.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMembers%20of%20SAG-AFTRA%20are%20permitted%20to%20promote%20new%20projects%20released%20during%20the%20strike%20if%20they%20meet%20the%20union's%20demands.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Swift%20is%20shaking%20off%20Hollywood's%20current%20strike%20stalemate%C2%A0between%20workers%20and%20studios%20for%20her%20upcoming%20blockbuster%20concert%20film%20%E2%80%94%20by%20simply%20agreeing%20to%20actors'%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift's%20Eras%20Tour%20concert%20film%20is%20set%20to%20be%20released%20in%20theaters%20on%20October%2013%20and%20is%20reportedly%20on%20track%20to%20make%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Ftaylor-swift-eras-tour-concert-film-could-open-with-100-million.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20million%20in%20its%20first%20weekend%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20has%20the%20union%20stamp%20of%20approval%3A%20Swift%20was%20able%20to%20strike%20an%20interim%20agreement%20with%20SAG-AFTRA%2C%20the%20actors'%20union%20of%20which%20she's%20a%20member.%20That%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sagaftrastrike.org%2F_files%2Fugd%2Fc68f5e_5b698b94503c47008b3e9f4db1b4d6da.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeans%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0Swift%20agreed%20to%20the%20union's%20last%20offers%20to%20studios%2C%20which%20include%20higher%20pay%2C%20increased%20breaks%2C%20and%20better%20residuals%20for%20streaming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20came%20to%20us%20and%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20do%20this%2C%20but%20only%20if%20she%20could%20do%20it%20the%20right%20way%20under%20a%20union%20contract.%20And%20we%20said%2C%20that's%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Duncan%20Crabtree-Ireland%2C%20SAG-AFTRA's%20national%20executive%20director%20and%20chief%20negotiator%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiewire.com%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-news%2Ftaylor-swift-movie-sag-agreement-duncan-crabtree-ireland-1234903987%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndieWire%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Toronto%20International%20Film%20Festival.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20she%20fulfilled%20all%20the%20same%20criteria%20as%20anybody%20else%20and%20has%20an%20interim%20agreement%20for%20that%20production.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterim%20agreements%20have%20become%20one%20potent%20strategic%20tool%20for%20striking%20actors.%20SAG-AFTRA%20joined%20writers%20on%20strike%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhollywood-strike-sag-aftra-wga-writers-actors-1960-2023-7%5C%22%3EJuly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20simultaneous%20labor%20action%20unseen%20since%201960.%20That%20means%20that%20actors%20aren't%20filming%20or%20doing%20media%20appearances%20to%20help%20promote%20their%20already-completed%20films.%20Negotiations%20with%20the%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%20(AMPTP)%2C%20the%20trade%20association%20that%20represents%20movie%20studios%20and%20major%20TV%20and%20streaming%20networks%2C%20did%20not%20result%20in%20an%20agreement%2C%20triggering%20a%20strike%20among%20SAG-AFTRA's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-sag-aftra-actors-wga-writers-unions-strike-hollywood%5C%22%3E160%2C000%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20studios%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sending%20countless%20actors%20out%20onto%20the%20picket%20lines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20independent%20productions%20can%20apply%20for%20interim%20agreements%2C%20where%20they%20agree%20to%20meet%20the%20union's%20demands.%20In%20cases%20where%20the%20union%20verifies%20that%20productions%20have%20cleared%20that%20bar%20actors%20can%20promote%20their%20work.%20Crabtree-Ireland%20has%20said%20that%20the%20union%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsag-aftra-interim-agreement-confusion-1235585788%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20received%201%2C400%20applications%20for%20interim%20agreements%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20has%20actively%20encouraged%20actors%20to%20promote%20and%20audition%20for%20productions%20that%20have%20been%20approved%20for%20an%20agreement%2C%20partially%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sagaftrastrike.org%2F_files%2Fugd%2Fc68f5e_5b698b94503c47008b3e9f4db1b4d6da.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20attempt%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20%26quot%3Bcompetitive%20pressure%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20major%20studios%20and%20showcase%20that%20%26quot%3Bstudios%20are%20shutting%20the%20industry%20down%20to%20resist%20terms%20that%20are%20clearly%20reasonable%20and%20viable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Agreement%20demonstrates%20to%20the%20AMPTP%20and%20the%20struck%20companies%20that%20independent%20producers%20at%20all%20budget%20levels%20are%20eager%2C%20keen%2C%20and%20able%20to%20work%20with%20our%20members%20under%20these%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20Crabtree-Ireland%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sagaftra.org%2Fvenice-telluride-toronto-and-beyond-sag-aftra-encourages-members-promote-approved-interim-agreement%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elate%20August%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20prominent%20stars%20like%20Jessica%20Chastain%20are%20promoting%20their%20work%20on%20productions%20approved%20for%20those%20agreements.%20Chastain%20took%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjes_chastain%2Fstatus%2F1700881775721877998%3Fs%3D46%26t%3D7dEMLEvmtKbqI2lGLTp4lQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20to%20write%20that%20if%20a%20majority%20of%20independent%20producers%20signed%20interim%20agreement%20deals%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20show%20the%20AMPTP%20how%20wrong%20they%20are%20when%20they%20say%20our%20contract%20terms%20are%20unrealistic%20or%20unreasonable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Swift%20and%20SAG-AFTRA%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20Swift's%20interim%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwift%20already%20sidestepped%20studios%20for%20her%20film%2C%20choosing%20to%20distribute%20it%20instead%20with%20AMC%20Theatres.%20As%20Insider's%20Jason%20Guerrasio%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-taylor-swift-eras-tour-got-into-movie-theaters-amc-2023-9%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that's%20a%20unique%20deal%20that%20could%20set%20up%20more%20trouble%20for%20studios%2C%20with%20one%20studio%20source%20telling%20Guerassio%20that%20it's%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20scary%26quot%3B%20to%20have%20a%20non-studio%20distributing%20the%20already%20highly%20anticipated%20film.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20interim%20agreement%20in%20place%2C%20Swift%20will%20be%20able%20to%20promote%20the%20film%20without%20crossing%20any%20picket%20lines.%20That%20might%20only%20boost%20an%20already%20huge%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20very%20excited%20for%20everyone%20to%20go%20see%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Crabtree-Ireland%20told%20IndieWire.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20judging%20by%20the%20success%20of%20the%20tour%2C%20I%20have%20every%20expectation%20that%20all%20the%20people%20who%20couldn't%20get%20tickets%20because%20they%20were%20so%20expensive%20or%20hard%20to%20get%2C%20like%20me%2C%20will%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20see%20it%20in%20the%20theaters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessin