2%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22externalLink%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.today.com%2Fhealth%2Fmom-chatgpt-diagnosis-pain-rcna101843%5C%22%20data-component%3D%5C%22link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EToday%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Courtney%20revealed%20that%20her%20four-year-old%20son%C2%A0Alex%20was%20suffering%20from%20toothache%2C%20''gigantic%20meltdowns''%2C%20and%20was%20also%20not%20growing%20in%20height.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20started%20chewing%20things%2C%20she%20took%20him%20to%20the%20dentist%2C%20wondering%20if%20his%20molars%20were%20coming%20in%20and%20causing%20pain.%C2%A0The%20dentist%20''ruled%20everything%20out''%20and%20suggested%20her%20to%20visit%20an%20orthodontist%20specializing%20in%20airway%20obstruction.%C2%A0The%20orthodontist%20found%20that%20Alex's%20palate%20was%20too%20small%20for%20his%20mouth%20and%20teeth%2C%20which%20made%20it%20tougher%20for%20him%20to%20breathe%20at%20night.%20He%20was%20given%20an%20expander%2C%20which%20only%20helped%20him%20briefly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourtney%20then%C2%A0noticed%20Alex%20had%20stopped%20growing%20taller%2C%20so%20they%20visited%20the%20pediatrician%2C%20who%20said%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20pandemic%20aftereffect%20and%20thereafter%20suggested%20physical%20therapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20before%20starting%20physical%20therapy%2C%20Alex%20started%20experiencing%20severe%20headaches%2C%20and%20a%20neurologist%2C%20said%20he%20had%20migraines.%20He%20also%20saw%20an%20ear%2C%20nose%2C%20and%20throat%20specialist%20to%20see%20if%20his%20sleep%20problems%20were%20due%20to%20his%20sinus%20cavities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20visiting%2017%20doctors%2C%C2%A0over%20three%20years%2C%20Alex's%20issue%20still%20had%20no%20diagnosis%20that%20explained%20all%20his%20symptoms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20saw%20so%20many%20doctors.%20We%20ended%20up%20in%20the%20ER%20at%20one%20point.%20I%20kept%20pushing.%20Nobody's%20willing%20to%20solve%20the%20greater%20problem.%20Nobody%20will%20even%20give%20you%20a%20clue%20about%20what%20the%20diagnosis%20could%20be%2C''%20Courtney%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrustrated%2C%20she%20then%20sought%20help%20from%20an%20unlikely%20source%20and%20signed%20up%20for%20ChatGPT%2C%20where%20she%C2%A0shared%20her%20son's%20symptoms%20and%20all%20the%20information%20from%20medical%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20went%20line%20by%20line%20of%20everything%20that%20was%20in%20his%20(MRI%20notes)%20and%20plugged%20it%20into%20ChatGPT.%20I%20put%20the%20note%20in%20there%20about%20...%20how%20he%20wouldn't%20sit%20crisscross%20applesauce.%20To%20me%2C%20that%20was%20a%20huge%20trigger%20(that)%20a%20structural%20thing%20could%20be%20wrong%2C''%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20ChatGPT%20suggested%20Alex%20was%20suffering%20from%20a%20rare%20neurological%20condition%20called%20tethered%20cord%20syndrome.%20She%20then%20found%20a%20Facebook%20group%20for%20families%20of%20children%20with%20tethered%20cord%20syndrome%20and%20later%20visited%20a%20neurosurgeon%20who%20examined%20Alex's%20MRI%20images%20and%20figured%20out%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlex%20underwent%20surgery%20to%20fix%20his%20tethered%20cord%20syndrome%C2%A0a%20few%20weeks%20ago%20and%20is%20now%20recovering.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-source%3D%5C%22inlineLink%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-ordinal%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22externalLink%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aans.org%2Fen%2FPatients%2FNeurosurgical-Conditions-and-Treatments%2FTethered-Spinal-Cord-Syndrome%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTethered%2520spinal%2520cord%2520syndrome%2520is%2Cclosely%2520associated%2520with%2520spina%2520bifida.%5C%22%20data-component%3D%5C%22link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Association%20of%20Neurological%20Surgeons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20tethered%20spinal%20cord%20syndrome%20is%20a%20neurologic%20disorder%20caused%20by%20tissue%20attachments%20that%20limit%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20spinal%20cord%20within%20the%20spinal%20column.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694513100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F6uld4jdg_chatgpt-getty_625x300_17_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-claims-she-found-correct-diagnosis-for-son-on-chatgpt-after-visiting-17-doctors-4382563%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20signed%20up%20for%20ChatGPT%2C%20where%20she%20shared%20her%20son's%20symptoms%20and%20all%20the%20information%20from%20medical%20reports.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-claims-she-found-correct-diagnosis-for-son-on-chatgpt-after-visiting-17-doctors-4382563%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-claims-she-found-correct-diagnosis-for-son-on-chatgpt-after-visiting-17-doctors-4382563%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fwoman-claims-she-found-correct-diagnosis-for-son-on-chatgpt-after-visiting-17-doctors-4382563%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20breaches%2010%2C000-run%20mark%20in%20ODIs%20to%20enter%20elite%20club%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694512962000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103605072%2Cimgsize-54504.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fasia-cup%2Frohit-sharma-breaches-10000-run-mark-in-odis-to-enter-elite-club%2Farticleshow%2F103605082.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20on%20Tuesday%20entered%20the%20exclusive%20club%2C%20becoming%20the%20sixth%20Indian%20batter%20to%20cross%20the%2010%2C000-run%20mark%20in%20ODIs.%20Rohit%20achieved%20the%20feat%20in%20India's%20Asia%20Cup%20second%20Super%20Four%20clash%20against%20Sri%20Lan