w.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkarnataka%2F133-crore-women-enrolled-gruha-lakshmi-is-one-of-indias-biggest-scheme-says-karnataka-cm-siddaramaiah%2Farticle67244187.ece%5C%22%3Elargest%20cash%20transfer%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20country%20introduced%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Fcentre-works-for-billionaires-says-rahul-as-karnataka-govt-unveils-gruha-lakshmi-scheme-101693385603813.html%5C%22%3E5%2C5000%20panchayats%20in%20the%20state%20with%20a%20coverage%20of%201.9%20crore%20women%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20are%20already%20enrolled%20for%20the%20scheme.%20The%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20other%20social%20protection%20schemes%20introduced%20by%20the%20newly%20elected%20Congress%20government%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20asserts%20that%20the%20implementation%20of%20these%20schemes%20will%20make%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fkarnataka%2Fkarnataka-govt-launches-gruha-jyothi-scheme-cm-says-bjp-made-country-bankrupt-1244027.html%5C%22%3Estate%20bankrupt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20expressed%20its%20disapproval%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20involving%20the%20transfer%20of%20money%20or%20free%20goods.%20Dubbing%20welfare%20schemes%20as%20%E2%80%9Crevadi%20culture%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0%20or%20in%20other%20words%2C%20%E2%80%98freebies%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frevdi-culture-welfare-narendra-modi%5C%22%3Edisguised%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20opponents%20in%20various%20states.%20However%2C%20the%20allegations%20of%20fiscal%20imprudence%20does%20not%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20objectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fkarnataka-accidental-pioneer-cash-transfers-for-food%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20Becomes%20an%20Accidental%20Pioneer%20of%20Cash%20Transfers%20for%20Food%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20despite%20the%20implementation%20of%20several%20welfare%20measures%20by%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20it%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-fiscally-prudent-is-delhis-aap-government-really%5C%22%3Eshown%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20for%20the%20period%202013-14%20to%202017-18%2C%20there%20was%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20public%20debt%20to%20the%20Gross%20State%20Domestic%20Product%20(GSDP)%20from%207.23%25%20to%204.89%25%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotwithstanding%20the%20uncritical%20political%20slandering%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20an%20argument%20can%20be%20made%20that%20an%20objective%20and%20nuanced%20understanding%20of%20the%20social%20objectives%20behind%20cash%20transfers%20is%20needed%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20are%20targeted%20towards%20a%20particular%20sub-section%20such%20as%20women.%20This%20should%20be%20done%20in%20the%20light%20of%20context-specific%20realities%20of%20women%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20embedded%20in%20a%20socio-political%20and%20cultural%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20analyses%20in%20the%20subsequent%20paragraphs%20will%20illuminate%20why%20affirmative%20action%20through%20cash%20transfers%20is%20a%20viable%20redistributive%20strategy%20and%20the%20specific%20role%20that%20cash%20transfers%20could%20play%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20lives%20in%20terms%20of%20reducing%20physical%20violence%20and%20empowering%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20affirmative%20action%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20concern%20that%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FSundayapp%2FpJdRTr4eBlaCIUVMKggVDM%2FCash-transfers-Miracle-or-mirage.html%5C%22%3Eraised%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20policy%20circles%20regarding%20cash%20transfers%20is%20that%20it%20may%20be%20a%20step%20towards%20state%20withdrawal%20from%20many%20essential%20services%20such%20as%20food%2C%20nutrition%2C%20health%2C%20and%20education.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20recently%20introduced%20welfare%20schemes%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government%2C%20cash%20transfers%20through%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20is%20supplemented%20with%20in-kind%20distribution%20of%20commodities%20and%20services.%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20Sakthi%20scheme%20provides%20free%20transport%20to%20all%20women%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20economic%20class%2C%20to%20travel%20in%20non-premium%20state%20buses%20and%20the%20Gruha%20Jyoti%20scheme%20provides%20up%20to%20200%20units%20of%20free%20power%20to%20households%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECash%20transfers%20to%20women%20can%20also%20be%20justified%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20social%20injustices%20and%20economic%20marginalisation%20faced%20by%20women.%20The%20Global%20Gender%20Gap%20Report%202023%20shows%20that%2C%20in%20the%20criteria%20%E2%80%98Economic%20Participation%20and%20Opportunity%E2%80%99%20(includes%20indicators%20like%20labour-force%20participation%20rate%2C%20wage%20equality%20for%20similar%20work%2C%20earned%20income%20etc.)%2C%20India%20has%20achieved%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Findia-climbs-eight-places-to-127-in-global-gender-index-says-wef-report%2Farticle66994156.ece%5C%22%3E36.7%25%20gender%20parity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20improvement%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fgender-equity-index-india-work-from-home-coronavirus-6968212%2F%5C%22%3Ewomen%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20a%20decrease%20in%20their%20unpaid%20domestic%20and%20care%20work%20or%20when%20such%20work%20is%20made%20more%20compatible%20with%20market%20work.%20However%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fwomen-spend-7-2-hours-on-unpaid-domestic-work-compared-to-2-8-hours-spent-by-men-iima-profs-research%2Farticleshow%2F97837422.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eevidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggests%20a%20highly%20unequal%20distribution%20of%20unpaid%20domestic%20work%20between%20men%20and%20women%2C%20with%20women%20spending%207.2%20hours%20on%20such%20work%20when%20compared%20to%20only%202.8%20hours%20spent%20by%20men%20in%20a%20day%2C%20thwarting%20attempts%20by%20women%20to%20engage%20in%20paid%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16082249%2F8554464586_33096a088a_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16082249%2F8554464586_33096a088a_c.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F16082249%2F8554464586_33096a088a_c-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-640721%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22534%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Haribai%2C%20an%20MGNREGA%20worker%20of%20Lalitpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20waits%20at%20a%20bank%20to%20collect%20her%20earnings.%20Photo%3A%20Photo%3A%20UN%20Women%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2F%20Flickr%20(CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20such%20evidence%2C%20cash%20transfers%20can%20alleviate%20the%20distress%20of%20economic%20insecurity%20faced%20by%20women%20and%20should%20be%20considered%20as%20a%20viable%20affirmative%20remedy.%20Besides%2C%20such%20transfers%20to%20women%20are%20also%20a%20way%20of%20creating%20discourse%20in%20the%20community%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20%E2%80%98natural%E2%80%99%20about%20the%20work%20that%20women%20do%20in%20the%20private%20sphere%20of%20the%20family%20and%20that%20housework%20also%20deserves%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20feared%20that%20unconditional%20cash%20transfers%20to%20women%20will%20re-enforce%20gender%20stereotypes%20and%20keep%20women%20away%20from%20seeking%20paid%20employment%20and%20further%20entrench%20them%20in%20household%20work%20but%20such%20concerns%20are%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2022%2F26-27%2Fcommentary%2Frevaluing-unpaid-work.html%5C%22%3Emisplaced%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Initiative%20for%20What%20Works%20to%20Advance%20Women%20and%20Girls%20in%20the%20Economy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwwage.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FKarnataka_Factsheet.pdf%5C%22%3E(IWWAGE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20that%20Karnataka%20has%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20female%20labour%20force%20participation%20(LFPR)%20in%20India.%20A%20small%20transfer%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20is%20unlikely%20to%20have%20any%20significant%20impact%20on%20their%20incentives%20to%20work.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fiwwage.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2FKarnataka_Factsheet.pdf%5C%22%3Edisaggregated%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20distribution%20of%20women%20workers%20in%20Karnataka%20by%20status%20of%20employment%20reveals%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20rural%20women%20are%20engaged%20in%20self-employment%20and%20casual%20labour.%20Around%2067%25%20of%20self-employed%20women%20are%20working%20only%20as%20unpaid%20workers%20in%20family%20enterprises%20in%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Finstead-of-withdrawing-food-security-a-minimum-income-guarantee-is-needed%5C%22%3EInstead%20of%20Withdrawing%20Food%20Security%2C%20a%20Minimum%20Income%20Guarantee%20Is%20Needed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20urban%20employed%20women%2C%20regular%20salaried%20jobs%20were%20most%20common%20but%20nearly%2062%25%20of%20such%20jobs%20were%20without%20any%20written%20job%20contract%20pointing%20to%20the%20precarity%20of%20such%20jobs.%20Women%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fit-is-getting-from-bad-to-worse-for-women-workers%2Farticle34574322.ece%5C%22%3Emore%20prone%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20job%20losses%20and%20less%20likely%20to%20fall%20back%20on%20new%20employment%20arrangements%20during%20economic%20shocks%2C%20as%20was%20observed%20during%20COVID-19.%20Hence%2C%20cash%20transfers%20can%20be%20a%20supplementary%20source%20of%20income%20to%20women%20as%20many%20are%20involved%20in%20non-paying%2C%20low-paying%20and%20precarious%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20and%20domestic%20violence%20against%20women%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-ians%2Fcash-transfers-prevent-intimate-partner-violence-study-118110600637_1.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20cash%20transfers%20to%20women%20have%20reduced%20intimate%20partner%20violence%20(IPV)%20against%20women.%20The%20evidence%20seems%20to%20suggest%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20poverty%20and%20economic%20insecurity%20as%20triggering%20factors%20for%20domestic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Karnataka%2C%2044%25%20of%20married%20women%20have%20experienced%20spousal%20violence%20as%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Fnhfs5-survey-data-karnataka-ranks-no-1-in-domestic-violence-cases-101652076272244.html%5C%22%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%20(NFHS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20for%20Karnataka.%20It%20is%20the%20highest%20among%20Indian%20states.%20The%20state%20has%20also%20witnessed%20the%20highest%20increase%20in%20domestic%20violence%20from%20the%20previous%20NFHS-4%20round.%20This%20paints%20a%20grim%20picture%20of%20gender-based%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%20If%20cash%20transfers%20help%20to%20reduce%20domestic%20violence%20as%20suggested%20in%20several%20studies%2C%20it%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20step%20forward%20towards%20gender%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECash%20transfers%20as%20pathways%20to%20women%20empowerment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fnfhs-5-data-womens-empowerment%5C%22%3Eimportant%20indicator%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20women%E2%80%99s%20empowerment%2C%20among%20several%20others%2C%20is%20household%20decision-making%2C%20ranging%20from%20what%20to%20cook%2C%20when%20to%20take%20a%20child%20to%20a%20health%20centre%2C%20to%20major%20purchase%20decisions%20in%20the%20household.%20Women%20are%20economically%20empowered%20only%20if%20they%20have%20control%20over%20the%20use%20of%20resources.%20However%2C%20restrictive%20gender%20norms%20and%20household%20dynamics%20often%20come%20in%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Women%20working%20on%20an%20NREGA%20site%20building%20a%20pond%20in%20Gopalpura%2C%20Jhabua%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Credit%3A%20UN%20Woman%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2FFlickr%20CC%20BY-NC-ND%202.0%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega-300x212.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega-768x542.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2Fmnrega-1024x722.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-75812%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Photo%3A%20UN%20Woman%2FGaganjit%20Singh%2FFlickr.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaspend.com%2Fwomen-more-likely-to-work-if-they-can-control-their-earnings-study%2F%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Yale%20University%20analysing%20the%20empowerment%20effects%2C%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20rights-based%20employment%20guarantee%20programme%20(MGNREGA)%2C%20showed%20that%20direct%20deposits%20of%20wages%20into%20women%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20a%20positive%20impact%20in%20shaping%20liberal%20attitudes%20towards%20work%20and%20in%20their%20engagement%20with%20paid%20work.%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20is%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20that%20women%20directly%20receive%20the%20money%20into%20their%20Aadhar-linked%20bank%20accounts%2C%20thus%2C%20enabling%20them%20to%20have%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20use%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fthe-evolution-of-indias-welfare-system-2008-to-2023%5C%22%3EThe%20Evolution%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Welfare%20System%2C%202008%20to%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20recognise%20the%20potential%20role%20of%20cash%20transfers%20in%20empowering%20women%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20especially%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20state%20has%20regressed%20on%20this%20front.%20There%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fblog%2Feconomy%2Fwhat-does-nfhs-5-data-tell-us-about-state-of-women-empowerment-in-india-80920%5C%22%3Edrop%20in%20the%20percentage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20ever%20married%20women%20who%20participate%20in%20household%20decisions%20(including%20health%20care%20for%20oneself%2C%20making%20major%20household%20purchases%20and%20visits%20to%20family%20or%20relatives)%20from%2082.7%25%20to%2080.4%25%20and%20Karnataka%20is%20one%20of%20the%20worst-performing%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20NFHS-4%20and%20NFHS-5%2C%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20drop%20in%20the%20percentage%20of%20women%20who%20engaged%20in%20any%20form%20of%20paid%20work%20from%2037%25%20to%2029%25.%20However%2C%20women%20having%20mobile%20phones%20they%20themselves%20use%20increased%20from%2047.1%25%20to%2061.8%25.%20This%20may%20augur%20well%20for%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20the%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20scheme%2C%20provided%20adequate%20financial%20and%20digital%20literacy%20is%20provided%20to%20women%20to%20operate%20their%20mobile-linked%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20whole%2C%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20welfare%20scheme%20Gruha%20Lakshmi%20is%20a%20welcome%20step.%20It%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20the%20recognition%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20contributions%20and%20the%20hope%20is%20that%20the%20financial%20support%20would%20improve%20their%20participation%20in%20paid%20work%2C%20household%20decisions%20and%20public%20life.%20However%2C%20this%20comes%20with%20a%20caveat.%20It%20is%20not%20enough%20that%20cash%20reaches%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20women%3B%20the%20financial%20infrastructure%20of%20the%20state%20should%20ensure%20easy%20accessibility.%20As%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcse.azimpremjiuniversity.edu.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F05%2FState_of_Working_India_2021-One_year_of_Covid-19.pdf%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20there%20can%20be%20rejections%20while%20accessing%20payments%20with%20no%20clear%20reason%2C%20necessitating%20multiple%20visits%20to%20banks.%20Such%20glitches%20should%20be%20avoided%20given%20that%20Indian%20women%20are%20faced%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fpageturner%2Fexcerpt%2Ftime-poverty-is-making-indian-women-lose-more-money-than-ever%2F515811%2F%5C%22%3Etime%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDivya%20Pradeep%20teaches%20Economics%20at%20CHRIST%20(Deemed%20to%20be%20University)%2C%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694512848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12134548%2FThe-Wire-5.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fgruha-lakshmi-despite-flak-karnataka-cash-transfer-scheme-is-a-powerful-tool-to-empower-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Led%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20criticism%20against%20welfare%20schemes%20involving%20the%20transfer%20of%20money%20or%20free%20goods.%20But%2C%20research%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20from%20across%20India%2C%20shows%20that%20cash%20transfers%20act%20as%20a%20viable%20redistributive%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Freelancer%3A%20Anupam%20debuts%20new%20look%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694512803000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103604651%2Cimgsize-43978.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthe-freelancer-anupam-kher-steals-the-show-with-his-unique-look-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F103604651.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103604651.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20actor%20Anupam%20Kher%20continues%20to%20surprise%20his%20audience%20with%20his%20versatility%20and%20new%20looks.%20His%20recent%20appearance%20in%20the%20show%20'The%20Freelancer'%20has%20left%20people%20in%20awe%20of%20his%20character%2C%20Dr%20Khan.%20Kher's%20collaboration%20with%20director%20Neeraj%20Pandey%20has%20always%20been%20successful%2C%20with%20the%20actor%20delivering%20memorable%20performances%20in%20films%20like%20'Special%2026'%20and%20'A%20Wednesday'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthe-freelancer-anupam-kher-steals-the-show-with-his-unique-look-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F103604651.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20single%20hard-charging%20CEO%20helped%20the%20US%20dollar%20take%20over%20the%20world%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20collage%20of%20the%20history%20of%20Citibank.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f9f75756f5190019fd0d93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBy%20building%20a%20global%20bank%2C%20Citibank%20helped%20the%20US%20dollar%20become%20dominant.%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWalter%20Wriston%20was%20once%20one%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20people%20on%20the%20planet.%20The%20chairman%20of%20the%20financial%20giant%20Citibank%20and%20its%20parent%20corporation%2C%20Citicorp%2C%20he%20was%20also%20a%20man%20with%20a%20vision.%20Wriston%20was%20a%20globalist%20who%20was%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20economist%20Friedrich%20Hayek's%20vision%20of%20a%20world%20in%20which%20market%20freedoms%20were%20the%20basis%20of%20individual%20liberty.%20Look%20closely%20at%20the%20burgeoning%20of%20international%20finance%2C%20of%20information%20networks%2C%20of%20logistical%20innovations%20that%20transformed%20trade.%20You'll%20find%20Wriston%20everywhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriston's%20financial%20innovations%20helped%20create%20the%20modern%20Eurodollar%20market%20%E2%80%94%20a%20vast%20offshore%20realm%20of%20financial%20transactions%20in%20US%20dollars%20happening%20outside%20of%20US%20borders.%20His%20efforts%20to%20build%20a%20private%20global%20payments%20system%20under%20Citibank's%20control%20in%20the%20early%201970s%20prompted%20other%20banks%20to%20build%20their%20own%20collective%20system%2C%20so%20as%20to%20avoid%20being%20drawn%20inside%20Citibank's%20gently%20smiling%20jaws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriston's%20willingness%20to%20put%20his%20ideas%20into%20action%20changed%20the%20world.%20As%20he%20explained%20in%201979%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bcurrent%20banking%20network%2C%20with%20its%20Euromarkets%20and%20its%20automated%20payments%20system%26quot%3B%20seemed%20dull%20and%20technical%2C%20but%20it%20had%20immense%20political%20consequences.%20He%20believed%20that%20if%20money%20could%20move%20rapidly%20from%20country%20to%20country%2C%20it%20could%20no%20longer%20be%20mastered%20by%20nations.%20Instead%20it%20might%20master%20them%2C%20replacing%20the%20whimsical%20tyranny%20of%20political%20rulers%20with%20the%20austere%20rigor%20of%20market%20discipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20tragedy%20of%20globalization%20was%20that%20men%20and%20women%20like%20Wriston%20built%20a%20world%20that%20seemed%20to%20escape%20the%20control%20of%20government%20but%20in%20fact%20was%20wide%20open%20to%20government%20power%20and%20its%20own%20undoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20clattering%20steampunk%20engine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20Wriston's%20career%2C%20in%20the%201960s%2C%20international%20banking%20barely%20existed.%20It%20was%20sluggish%2C%20timid%2C%20and%20lazy.%20Banks%20were%20trapped%20inside%20national%20borders%20by%20complex%20and%20clashing%20rules%20put%20in%20place%20after%20the%20financial%20crash%20of%20the%20Great%20Depression.%20These%20regulations%20meant%20that%20most%20banks%20faced%20little%20international%20competition%20and%20had%20scant%20incentive%20to%20invest%20in%20new%20ways%20of%20doing%20things.%20It%20was%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20be%20a%20true%20international%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%201960s%20banking%20industry%20was%20a%20Victorian%20relic%20in%20the%20modern%20era%2C%20a%20clattering%20steampunk%20engine%20of%20rusting%20pistons%20and%20gutta-percha-covered%20cables%2C%20with%20a%20few%20incongruously%20modern%20parts%20bolted%20on.%20Eric%20Sepkes%2C%20who%20helped%20build%20the%20European%20payments%20system%2C%20later%20recalled%20how%20Citibank's%20London%20operation%20relied%20on%20a%20system%20of%20pneumatic%20tubes%20to%20communicate%20between%20the%20office%20that%20initiated%20the%20payments%20to%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20borrowers%2C%20business%2C%20brokers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20office%20that%20authorized%20those%20payments.%20Staff%20had%20to%20handwrite%20payment%20instructions%20on%20a%20form%2C%20which%20they%20then%20stuffed%20into%20a%20canister%20and%20inserted%20into%20a%20partial%20vacuum%20conduit%20that%20ferried%20it%20to%20its%20destination%20where%20the%20authorizes%20would%20then%20release%20the%20funds%20(the%20City%20of%20London%20had%20built%20miles%20of%20pneumatic%20tube%20networks%20in%20the%20nineteenth%20century).%20One%20day%2C%20when%20the%20payments%20people%20didn't%20hear%20back%20from%20authorization%2C%20they%20discovered%20that%20the%20tube%20had%20become%20blocked.%20Citibank%20had%20to%20call%20in%20a%20chimney%20sweep%20to%20fix%20the%20problem%2C%20re-enabling%20payments%20processing%20for%20the%20entire%20continent%20of%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EWith%20proper%20technology%2C%20the%20dull-seeming%20backroom%20activities%20of%20banking%20such%20as%20payments%20processing%20could%20become%20a%20source%20of%20profit%20and%20power.%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EGlobal%20banking%20was%20a%20system%20of%20mysterious%20tubes%20on%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%2C%20with%20various%20portals%20that%20took%20money%20in%2C%20did%20expensive%20and%20incomprehensible%20things%20to%20it%2C%20and%20spat%20it%20out%20somewhere%20else.%20No%20one%20fully%20understood%20the%20machinery%2C%20least%20of%20all%20the%20people%20who%20were%20supposedly%20in%20charge.%20The%20gentlemanly%20activities%20of%20merchant%20banking%2C%20where%20men%20with%20excellent%20pedigrees%20built%20on%20their%20social%20connections%20to%20win%20deals%2C%20remained%20rigidly%20distinct%20from%20the%20mundane%20tasks%20of%20payments%20processing%2C%20which%20were%20performed%20by%20female%20clerks%20surrounded%20by%20vast%20piles%20of%20paper.%20It%20took%20a%20very%20long%20time%20to%20send%20money%20across%20borders.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20inflation%20in%20Argentina%20was%20rising%20so%20rapidly%20that%20Citibank's%20branch%20in%20the%20country%20had%20to%20convert%20its%20profits%20into%20cases%20of%20Scotch%20whisky%20to%20prevent%20the%20value%20of%20the%20income%20from%20being%20inflated%20away%20before%20they%20could%20be%20sent%20to%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriston%20helped%20rebuild%20this%20clanking%20machine%20into%20an%20engine%20of%20transformation%2C%20welding%20disjointed%20national%20markets%20into%20a%20true%20world%20economy.%20His%20strategy%20was%20built%20around%20two%20insights.%20The%20first%20was%20that%20global%20markets%20could%20%E2%80%94%20if%20they%20were%20allowed%20%E2%80%94%20circumvent%20the%20labyrinthine%20systems%20of%20rules%20constructed%20by%20national%20regulators%20and%20eventually%20replace%20them.%20The%20second%20was%20that%20banking%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbranch%20of%20the%20information%20business.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarket%20prices%20provided%20one%20crucial%20source%20of%20information%2C%20summarizing%20as%20they%20did%20the%20decisions%20of%20millions%20of%20individuals%20over%20what%20to%20buy%20and%20sell.%20Technology%20provided%20another%2C%20allowing%20banks%20to%20discover%20the%20information%20they%20had%20buried%20within%20their%20own%20bureaucracies%20and%20to%20better%20exchange%20information%20with%20each%20other%20and%20their%20customers.%20With%20proper%20technology%2C%20the%20dull-seeming%20backroom%20activities%20of%20banking%20such%20as%20payments%20processing%20could%20become%20a%20source%20of%20profit%20and%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Wriston%20began%20to%20remake%20Citibank%2C%20money%20had%20already%20begun%20to%20seep%20through%20the%20seams%20in%20the%20ductwork.%20Businesses%20outside%20the%20United%20States%20desperately%20wanted%20US%20dollars%2C%20which%20were%20needed%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20oil%2C%20while%20businesses%20in%20the%20United%20States%20wanted%20to%20earn%20higher%20returns.%20US%20regulators%20had%20capped%20interest%20rates%20for%20ordinary%20consumers%20and%20stopped%20interest%20payments%20altogether%20on%20corporate%20deposits%2C%20limiting%20the%20profits%20many%20stateside%20banks%20could%20earn.%20Bankers%20had%20already%20begun%20to%20figure%20out%20crafty%20means%20to%20connect%20overseas%20dollar%20demand%20to%20American%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWriston%20and%20his%20colleagues%20built%20the%20institutional%20infrastructures%20that%20allowed%20this%20to%20happen%20at%20scale.%20They%20created%20financial%20instruments%20like%20the%20certificate%20of%20deposit%2C%20which%20provided%20a%20legal%20pipeline%20to%20smoothly%20convey%20the%20dollars%20owned%20by%20American%20businesses%20to%20the%20international%20banks%20that%20needed%20them%20for%20their%20customers.%20Citibank's%20competitors%2C%20like%20JPMorgan%20and%20Warburg%2C%20adapted%20these%20instruments%20and%20came%20up%20with%20their%20own%20ideas.%20What%20was%20once%20a%20small%20and%20disconnected%20trade%20in%20Eurodollars%2C%20based%20primarily%20in%20London%2C%20became%20a%20vast%20marketplace%20for%20buying%2C%20selling%2C%20and%20lending%20in%20dollars%20outside%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20political%20economist%20Eric%20Helleiner%20describes%20it%2C%20the%20Eurodollar%20market%20became%20a%20legal%20gray%20zone%20where%20vast%20amounts%20of%20US%20dollars%20circulated%20beyond%20US%20borders.%20As%20the%20market%20grew%2C%20the%20US%20dollar%20became%20established%20as%20the%20universal%20basis%20of%20international%20trade.%20If%20you%20were%20a%20Japanese%20company%20selling%20goods%20to%20a%20business%20in%20Italy%2C%20it%20was%20hard%20to%20convert%20the%20Italian%20lira%20that%20you%20were%20paid%20in%20directly%20into%20Japanese%20yen.%20The%20economic%20relationship%20between%20Japan%20and%20Italy%20wasn't%20big%20enough%20to%20support%20a%20liquid%20market%20where%20the%20two%20currencies%20could%20be%20exchanged%20directly.%20The%20Eurodollar%20market%20provided%20an%20easy%20detour%2C%20where%20you%20could%20turn%20lira%20into%20dollars%20and%20then%20dollars%20into%20yen.%20And%20as%20the%20supply%20of%20Eurodollars%20grew%2C%20it%20increasingly%20made%20sense%20for%20companies%20to%20simply%20buy%20and%20sell%20in%20dollars%2C%20which%20they%20could%20then%20convert%20into%20their%20home%20currencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EThe%20dollar%20became%20a%20global%20currency%2C%20without%20anyone%20really%20planning%20it.%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20result%20was%20that%20the%20dollar%20became%20a%20global%20currency%2C%20without%20anyone%20really%20planning%20it.%20More%20dollars%20circulated%20outside%20the%20United%20States%20than%20within%20it.%20US%20officials%20at%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20and%20elsewhere%20paid%20surprisingly%20little%20official%20attention%20to%20what%20was%20happening.%20This%20made%20the%20market%20attractive%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20the%20Soviet%20Union%2C%20which%20needed%20dollars%20for%20international%20trade%20but%20worried%20that%20they%20might%20be%20seized%20by%20the%20US%20government%20if%20they%20were%20deposited%20directly%20in%20American%20banks.%20By%20using%20Eurodollars%2C%20which%20were%20bought%20and%20sold%20in%20London%20and%20Italy%2C%20they%20thought%20they%20could%20avoid%20this%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20markets%20all%20depended%20on%20an%20infrastructure%20of%20clever%20financial%20engineering.%20Banks%20weren't%20trading%20physical%20stacks%20of%20hundred-dollar%20bills.%20Looked%20at%20closely%2C%20Eurodollars%20were%20an%20accounting%20fiction%2C%20imaginary%20dollars%20traded%20between%20real%20banks.%20They%20couldn't%20be%20used%20for%20anything%20other%20than%20buying%20other%20currencies.%20But%20every%20single%20Eurodollar%20had%20to%20be%20backed%20by%20a%20real%20dollar%2C%20sitting%20in%20a%20US%20bank%20operating%20under%20US%20law%20and%20responsible%20to%20US%20regulators.%20As%20Wriston%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20the%20dollars%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20except%20%5Bphysical%5D%20currency%20%E2%80%94%20are%20deposits%20in%20a%20bank%20in%20America%2C%20because%20that%20is%20the%20only%20place%20anyone%20can%20spend%20a%20dollar.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221838%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Underground%20Empire%3A%20How%20America%20Weaponized%20The%20World%20Economy%20cover%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8957a04e14000196cdf57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222775%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUnderground%20Empire%3A%20How%20America%20Weaponized%20the%20World%20Economy%3Cp%3EHenry%20Holt%20and%20Company%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20that%20transactions%20using%20Eurodollars%20had%20to%20be%20cleared%20through%20a%20US%20bank's%20internal%20processes%20(moving%20money%20from%20one%20customer's%20account%20to%20another's)%20or%20through%20a%20clearing%20institution%20run%20by%20US%20banks%2C%20such%20as%20CHIPS%2C%20the%20Clearing%20House%20Interbank%20Payments%20System.%20Foreign%20banks%20had%20to%20maintain%20clearing%20accounts%20in%20US%20financial%20institutions%20if%20they%20were%20to%20trade%20dollars%20and%20participate%20in%20global%20finance.%20The%20Eurodollar%20market%20might%20indeed%20have%20been%20a%20pirate%20kingdom%2C%20but%20it%20was%20one%20where%20the%20buccaneers%20had%20to%20regularly%20provision%20themselves%20in%20the%20monarch's%20ports.%20The%20more%20that%20foreign%20banks%20came%20to%20depend%20on%20access%20to%20US%20dollars%2C%20the%20more%20vulnerable%20they%20were%20to%20US%20regulators%2C%20whenever%20those%20regulators%20finally%20woke%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGradually%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bdollar%20clearing%20system%26quot%3B%20run%20by%20US%20banks%20like%20Citibank%20and%20JPMorgan%20and%20clearing%20institutions%20like%20CHIPS%20became%20the%20beating%20heart%20of%20the%20world's%20financial%20system%2C%20circulating%20dollars%20around%20the%20world%20in%20a%20regular%20systole%20and%20diastole.%20The%20Eurodollar%20market%2C%20far%20from%20creating%20a%20decentered%20new%20realm%20of%20finance%2C%20had%20made%20the%20global%20financial%20system%20more%20fragile%20and%20more%20vulnerable%20to%20American%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EState-controlled%20financial%20system%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWriston%20had%20hoped%20to%20build%20a%20world%20where%20business%2C%20not%20government%2C%20was%20in%20charge.%20He%20and%20his%20peers%20helped%20markets%20spill%20over%20the%20confines%20of%20national%20borders%20into%20each%20other%2C%20a%20confluence%20that%20grew%20into%20a%20world%20ocean%20of%20information%2C%20money%2C%20and%20production.%20But%20even%20if%20business%20leaders%20like%20Wriston%20did%20not%20aspire%20to%20become%20sovereigns%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20build%20their%20own%20business%20empires.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201998%2C%20Helleiner%20wrote%20a%20skeptical%20riposte%20to%20Wriston's%20vision.%20It%20wasn't%20just%20that%20Eurodollar%20markets%20existed%20on%20the%20sufferance%20of%20governments%20and%20would%20have%20withered%20if%20the%20United%20States%20had%20not%20let%20them%20flourish.%20It%20was%20that%20global%20finance%20was%20%26quot%3Bincreasingly%20concentrated%26quot%3B%20in%20great%20financial%20centers%20like%20New%20York%20and%20London%20where%20electronic%20money%20had%20to%20pass%20through%20various%20%26quot%3Bcentral%20'choke%20points.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Helleiner%20speculated%2C%20this%20might%20actually%20increase%20the%20power%20of%20governments%20like%20the%20United%20States%20rather%20than%20undermining%20it.%20The%20question%20was%20when%20these%20governments%20would%20take%20up%20their%20power%2C%20and%20what%20they%20would%20do%20when%20they%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20of%20the%20September%2011%20attack%2C%20Helleiner's%20predictions%20began%20to%20become%20a%20reality.%20The%20US%20Department%20of%20the%20Treasury%20started%20to%20aggressively%20investigate%20its%20options%20for%20gathering%20financial%20data%20from%20the%20world%2C%20so%20that%20it%20could%20detect%20future%20attacks.%20One%20of%20the%20key%20areas%20to%20watch%2C%20the%20Treasury%20found%2C%20was%20the%20flow%20of%20dollars%20around%20the%20world.%20It%20began%20to%20develop%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20sanction%2C%20which%20used%20its%20control%20of%20%26quot%3Bdollar%20clearing%26quot%3B%20to%20force%20international%20banks%20to%20implement%20US%20policy%20outside%20its%20borders.%20The%20SWIFT%20(Society%20for%20Worldwide%20Interbank%20Financial%20Telecommunication)%20messaging%20system%20%E2%80%94%20which%20plays%20a%20core%20role%20in%20global%20financial%20transfers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20dollar%20clearing%20were%20combined%20to%20cut%20Iran%20out%20of%20the%20world's%20financial%20system%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20the%20negotiating%20table%20to%20discuss%20its%20nuclear%20weapons%20program.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20officials%20who%20planned%20these%20steps%20often%20thought%20of%20them%20as%20once-off%20emergency%20measures.%20But%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come%2C%20the%20US%20government%20would%20repeatedly%20exercise%20its%20power%20over%20the%20dollar%20to%20exact%20a%20financial%20toll%20on%20its%20geopolitical%20adversaries%20%E2%80%94%20including%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20its%20sanctions%20on%20Russia%20following%20the%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%20Instead%20of%20the%20stateless%2C%20government-less%20world%20that%20Wriston%20envisioned%2C%20the%20internationalization%20of%20the%20US%20dollar%20became%20the%20precedent%20for%20a%20massive%20transformation%20of%20America's%20financial%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fhenry-farrell%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fhenry-farrell%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EHenry%20Farrell%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20the%20SNF%20Agora%20Professor%20at%20Johns%20Hopkins%20SAIS%2C%20the%202019%20winner%20of%20the%20Friedrich%20Schiedel%20Prize%20for%20Politics%20and%20Technology%2C%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20The%20Monkey%20Cage%20at%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20and%20co-founder%20of%20the%20popular%20academic%20blog%2C%20Crooked%20Timber.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fabraham-newman%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fabraham-newman%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EAbraham%20Newman%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Foreign%20Service%20and%20Government%20Department%20at%20Georgetown%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExcerpted%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-61567-20%26h%3D9ac65c64576620a4184707df7bb43ef6afdc60b14eefb965ad895b7cee2deeb8%26postID%3D64e75dd9065a66ec8f7623dd%26postSlug%3Dhow-us-dollar-became-dominant-citibank-walter-wriston-2023-9%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FUnderground-Empire-America-Weaponized-Economy%