d%20communities%20who%20face%20prejudice%20and%20discrimination.%20It%20acknowledges%20that%20people%20of%20the%20South%20Asian%20origin%20do%20experience%20forms%20of%20racism.%20However%2C%20it%20says%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20campaign%20for%20the%20Hinduphobia%20Bill%20is%20part%20of%20larger%20efforts%20to%3Cbr%3E%5Cnsuppress%20discussion%20about%20the%20human%20rights%20violations%20in%20India%20and%20in%20Canada%20using%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20as%20a%20shield.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20campaign%20to%20recognise%20Hinduphobia%20is%20spearheaded%20by%20the%20dominant%20caste%20privileged%20South%20Asian%20diaspora%20who%20aim%20to%20obfuscate%20any%20discussion%20about%20the%20violence%20against%20Dalits%20(formerly%20untouchables)%2C%20Adivasis%20(Indigenous%20communities%20and%20tribes)%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%20in%20India.%20Claims%20of%20Hinduphobia%20have%20been%20used%20to%20persecute%2C%20hound%2C%20delegitimise%20and%20silence%20the%20fight%20against%20casteism%20and%20the%20oppression%20of%20minorities%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20caution%20you%20that%20supporting%20this%20petition%20will%20have%20a%20disastrous%20impact%20on%20the%20safety%20of%20religious%20minorities%2C%20caste-oppressed%20communities%20and%20human%20rights%20defenders%20in%20Canada%2C%20India%20and%20beyond%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20SADAN%2C%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20requested%20all%20the%20elected%20representatives%20to%20oppose%20the%20petition%20as%20a%20step%20towards%20ensuring%20that%20some%20of%20the%20most%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%2C%20in%20Canada%20and%20globally%2C%20remain%20protected%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20SADAN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20Canadian%20Organization%20for%20Hindu%20Heritage%20Education%2C%20calling%20upon%20the%20House%20to%20recognise%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20term%20in%20the%20glossary%20of%20terms%20in%20the%20Human%20Rights%20Code.%20The%20term%20aims%20to%20recognise%20anti-Hindu%20prejudice%20and%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D%20is%20defined%20as%20the%20denial%2C%20negation%2C%20prejudice%20or%20vilification%20against%20Hindus%2C%20Hinduism%2C%20or%20%E2%80%9CHinduness%E2%80%9D.%20The%20petition%20aims%20to%20raise%20awareness%20and%20address%20systemic%20and%20institutional%20%E2%80%9CHinduphobia%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F09191115%2Fimage-829.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisastrous-impact-on-minorities-safety-south-asian-diaspora-on-canadas-hinduphobia-petition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Claims%20of%20Hinduphobia%20have%20been%20used%20to%20persecute%2C%20hound%2C%20delegitimise%20and%20silence%20the%20fight%20against%20casteism%20and%20the%20oppression%20of%20minorities%20in%20India%2C'%20said%20the%20South%20Asian%20Dalit%20Adivasi%20Network%2C%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdisastrous-impact-on-minorities-safety-south-asian-diaspora-on-canadas-hinduphobia-petition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIVE%3A%20SpiceJet%20successfully%20pays%20Rs%20100%20crore%20to%20Kal%20Airways%20Private%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511747000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F25%2Ffull%2F1692964007-5579.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreaking-news-live-12-sept-latest-news-india-today-morocco-earthquake-123091200140_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Catch%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20across