0iPhone%2015s%20will%20come%20from%20China%2C%20that%20would%20be%20the%20first%20time%20a%20latest%20generation%2C%20India-assembled%20device%20is%20available%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20sale%2C%20they%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20matter%20is%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20also%20underscore%20India's%20growing%20production%20prowess%2C%20and%20reflect%20a%20significant%20departure%20from%20Apple's%20previous%20strategy%20of%20selling%20mostly%20Chinese-made%20new%20devices%20to%20frenzied%20customers%20across%20the%20world.%20The%20new%20iPhone%2015%20is%20expected%20to%20go%20on%20sale%20in%20the%20days%20or%20weeks%20after%20its%20unveiling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECupertino%2C%20California-based%20Apple%20began%20iPhone%2015%20production%20at%20supplier%20Foxconn%20Technology%20Group's%20factory%20in%20southern%20Tamil%20Nadu%20state%20last%20month.%20That%20move%20was%20yet%20another%20effort%20by%20the%20US%20tech%20giant%20to%20further%20narrow%20the%20gap%20between%20its%20India%20operations%20and%20its%20main%20manufacturing%20bases%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlight%20delays%20with%20the%20India-built%20device%20could%20occur%20because%20of%20unforeseen%20logistics%20bottlenecks%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20Apple%20representatives%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20set%20to%20introduce%20the%20iPhone%2015%2C%20updated%20watches%20and%20AirPods%20at%20a%20gala%20event%20at%20its%20US%20headquarters.%20Sales%20of%20new%20products%20begin%20typically%20around%2010%20days%20after%20the%20unveiling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20iPhone%2014%2C%20Apple%20assembled%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20its%20global%20output%20in%20India%2C%20which%20lagged%20behind%20China%20production%20by%20six%20to%20nine%20months.%20That%20delay%20was%20drastically%20reduced%20last%20year%20to%20just%20weeks%2C%20and%20Apple%20has%20increased%20the%20proportion%20of%20iPhones%20it%20assembles%20in%20India%20to%20reach%207%25%20at%20the%20end%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20financial%20incentives%20to%20boost%20local%20manufacturing%20and%20Apple's%20strategy%20to%20look%20beyond%20China%20have%20helped%20India%20become%20increasingly%20important%20to%20the%20iPhone%20maker's%20diversification%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20iPhone%2015%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20update%20to%20the%20device%20in%20three%20years.%20It%20will%20include%20upgrades%20to%20the%20camera%20system%20across%20the%20range%2C%20and%20the%20Pro%20models%20will%20gain%20an%20improved%203-nanometer%20processor.%20The%20new%20lineup%20is%20critical%20to%20reviving%20flagging%20sales.%20Apple%20in%20August%20reported%20its%20third%20straight%20quarter%20of%20declining%20sales%2C%20weighed%20down%20by%20tepid%20consumer%20demand%20in%20key%20markets%20like%20the%20US%2C%20China%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20Apple%20suppliers%20in%20India%20-%20Pegatron%20Corp.%20and%20a%20Wistron%20Corp.%20factory%20that%20is%20soon%20being%20acquired%20by%20the%20Tata%20Group%20-%20will%20also%20likely%20soon%20assemble%20the%20iPhone%2015%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20which%20opened%20its%20first%20India%20stores%20this%20year%2C%20views%20the%20fast-growing%20market%20as%20both%20a%20retail%20opportunity%20and%20an%20important%20production%20base%20for%20its%20gadgets%20in%20the%20longer%20term.%20In%20the%20quarter%20through%20June%2C%20iPhone%20sales%20in%20India%20grew%20at%20a%20double-digit%20rate%20to%20a%20new%20high%2C%20Apple%20said%20without%20revealing%20precise%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fl71dot9k_apple-reuters_625x300_30_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fiphone-15-apple-to-sell-made-in-india-iphones-on-launch-day-for-first-