xisting%20Parliament%20building.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20one%20need%20five%20days%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20a%20building%3F%20And%20why%20is%20there%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%9Cconsiderable%20speculation%E2%80%9D%20in%20a%20democracy%20when%20laws%20and%20changes%20should%20be%20discussed%20openly%20and%20transparently%3F%20On%20this%2C%20the%20report%20did%20not%20offer%20any%20enlightenment%20to%20readers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20special%20session%20was%20first%20announced%20on%20August%2031%2C%20there%20began%20a%20guessing%20game%20on%20why%20it%20was%20being%20called%20so%20shortly%20after%20one%20session%20had%20just%20ended%20on%20August%2011.%20The%20Winter%20Session%20will%20begin%20in%20November%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20there%20is%20no%20other%20time%20for%20Parliament%20to%20meet.%20Why%20again%20this%20month%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20said%20it%20was%20to%20change%20the%20name%20of%20the%20country%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fbharat-india-hindustan-history%5C%22%3EIndia%20to%20Bharat%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Two%20days%20of%20media%20focus%20went%20into%20that.%20Ministers%20defended%20the%20move%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20it%2C%20but%20were%20unable%20to%20confirm%20whether%20or%20not%20this%20change%20in%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20what%20the%20session%20was%20for.%20Another%20guess%20was%20that%20it%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill.%20This%20was%20originally%20passed%20by%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%202008%2C%20but%20since%20then%20it%20has%20stalled%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20support%20and%20demands%20of%20sub-reservations%20within%20this%20category%20for%20marginalised%20sections.%20If%20this%20is%20on%20the%20agenda%20and%20it%20goes%20through%2C%20it%20will%20set%20aside%20one-third%20of%20all%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%20for%20women.%20This%20is%20a%20considerable%20reform%2C%20and%20if%20it%20is%20indeed%20this%20law%20that%20is%20being%20taken%20up%2C%20one%20hopes%20that%20it%20passes.%20But%20of%20course%2C%20one%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20guess%20in%20the%20media%20was%20that%20the%20government%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20was%20calling%20the%20general%20election%20early.%20The%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20due%20in%20April-May%20next%20year%2C%20meaning%20in%20another%20seven%20to%20eight%20months%2C%20but%20they%20might%20be%20advanced%20just%20as%20the%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20government%20had%20done%20in%202004.%20This%20theory%20has%20not%20found%20many%20takers%2C%20but%20again%2C%20who%20knows%3F%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20gambit%20to%20call%20elections%20early%20did%20not%20succeed%20and%20the%20government%20fell%2C%20so%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20caution%20on%20this%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20fervent%20speculation%20was%20around%20something%20called%20%E2%80%9Cone%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20system%20whereby%20all%20states%20and%20the%20Centre%20will%20go%20into%20elections%20every%20five%20years%20together%20and%20citizens%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20Assembly%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20Will%20corporation%20elections%20also%20be%20included%3F%20One%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20about%20byelections%3F%20And%20how%20will%20the%20EVMs%20be%20set%20up%20for%20multiple%20elections%3F%20One%20does%20not%20know%20that%20either%2C%20but%20perhaps%20wiser%20minds%20have%20already%20sorted%20all%20such%20things%20out.%20A%20committee%20has%20been%20set%20up%20under%20a%20former%20President%20to%20look%20into%20the%20idea%2C%20but%20how%20this%20committee%20will%20meet%20and%20give%20its%20findings%20all%20in%20time%20for%20the%20special%20session%20is%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20more%20story%20floated%20in%20the%20media%20was%20that%20the%20session%20was%20about%20a%20commission%20set%20up%20in%202017%20to%20look%20at%20sub-categorisation%20of%20OBCs%20so%20that%20reservations%20could%20be%20made%20more%20equitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parliamentary%20form%20of%20government%20carries%20with%20it%20something%20called%20collective%20responsibility%2C%20meaning%20that%20decisions%20are%20jointly%20owned.%20But%20here%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20is%20as%20much%20in%20the%20dark%20about%20decisions%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us%20are.%20Two%20instances%20from%20the%20past%20will%20suffice%20to%20demonstrate%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20was%20a%20report%20from%20November%2010%2C%202016%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fdon-t-bring-your-phones-modi-s-cabinet-meet-that-took-everyone-by-surprise%2Fstory-YEbaMM3lr3McikFnnSZTmL.html%5C%22%3Eheadlined%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20bring%20your%20phones%3A%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Cabinet%20meet%20that%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise.%E2%80%9D%20The%20report%20said%20Union%20ministers%20found%20out%20about%20demonetisation%20the%20same%20day%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%20meaning%20that%20it%20was%20neither%20discussed%20nor%20debated.%20Another%20instance%20is%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20filing%20of%20over%20240%20Right%20to%20Information%20queries%20with%20the%20government%20about%20the%20national%20lockdown%20of%202020.%20It%20asked%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20departments%20of%20health%2C%20finance%2C%20disaster%20management%20and%20the%20rest%20about%20what%20they%20knew%20regarding%20the%20lockdown%20and%20how%20they%20prepared.%20The%20answer%20was%20that%20they%20did%20not%20know%20and%20did%20not%20prepare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20form%20of%20government%2C%20where%20secrets%20and%20major%20decisions%20are%20kept%20from%20the%20Cabinet%20itself%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20continuing%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20speculation%20around%20this%20special%20session.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20Question%20Hour%20either%20in%20this%20session%2C%20and%20while%20this%20is%20expected%2C%20it%20is%20not%20necessary.%20Even%20questions%20asked%20are%20not%20answered%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20so%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20stopping%20them%20from%20being%20asked%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20sent%20a%20list%20of%20things%20they%20would%20like%20discussed%20in%20the%20session.%20These%20include%20inflation%2C%20joblessness%2C%20MSP%20for%20farmers%2C%20the%20continuing%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Adani%20scandal%2C%20communal%20tensions%20across%20India%2C%20the%20Chinese%20actions%20in%20Ladakh%20and%20elsewhere%2C%20the%20need%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20(or%20any%20census%2C%20given%20that%20the%20primary%20one%20has%20been%20inexplicably%20delayed)%2C%20the%20strains%20on%20federalism%20and%20impact%20of%20natural%20disasters%20and%20climate%20change.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%2C%20assuming%20these%20are%20not%20already%20on%20the%20agenda%2C%20they%20will%20be%20taken%20up%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20even%20the%20Cabinet%20itself%20has%20such%20little%20say%20in%20what%20should%20be%20discussed%20and%20passed%2C%20why%20should%20the%20Opposition%20be%20listened%20to%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAakar%20Patel%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694511048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-issues-will-the-5-day-special-session-take-up-no-one-knows-not-even-the-cabinet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Winter%20Session%20will%20begin%20in%20November%2C%20so%20it%20is%20not%20as%20if%20there%20is%20no%20other%20time%20for%20Parliament%20to%20meet.%20Why%20again%20this%20month%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fans%20demand%20refund%20for%20Jawan%3B%20here's%20why!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2