%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20open%20up%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20there%20may%20be%20issues%20with%20importers%20as%20well.%20The%20government%20issued%20another%20clarification%2C%20requiring%20importers%20of%20pulses%20to%20compulsorily%20declare%20their%20available%20stocks.%20This%20step%20became%20necessary%20as%20several%20importers%20had%20been%20holding%20dal%20stocks%20after%20benefiting%20from%20relaxed%20import%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20government%20reduced%20import%20duties%20on%20dal%2C%20flooding%20the%20markets.%20But%20neither%20consumers%20nor%20farmers%20have%20benefited%20from%20this%20policy%20because%20importers%2C%20foreign%20traders%20and%20large%20stockholders%20have%20once%20again%20reaped%20the%20lion%E2%80%99s%20share%20of%20the%20imports%2C%20which%20is%20in%20their%20godowns.%20While%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20are%20commendable%2C%20they%20may%20not%20be%20sufficient%20to%20curb%20dal%20price%20inflation.%20In%20fact%2C%20some%20measures%20may%20inadvertently%20favour%20these%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20this%20the%20case%3F%20Firstly%2C%20the%20government%20allowed%20the%20cartel%20responsible%20for%20dal%20price%20manipulation%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%E2%80%99s%20report%2C%20to%20go%20unpunished.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20attempted%20to%20dismantle%20the%20Essential%20Commodities%20Act%20as%20part%20of%20the%20farm%20laws.%20A%C2%A0%3Cem%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0investigation%20initiated%20by%20the%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20was%20closed%20for%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20evidence%E2%80%9D.%20This%20raises%20questions%20about%20how%20two%20government%20departments%20could%20study%20the%20same%20problem%20and%20arrive%20at%20different%20conclusions.%20While%20the%20IT%20department%20found%20evidence%20of%20%E2%80%9Ccartelization%E2%80%9D%20and%20conducted%20an%20investigation%2C%20the%20CCI%2