n's%20behaviour%20with%20others%20she%20was%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3BCan't%20you%20take%20a%20joke%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20macho%20nature%20of%20Australian%20politics%20was%20highlighted%20in%20late%202021%20when%20a%20scathing%20review%20found%20the%20country's%20halls%20of%20power%20rife%20with%20heavy%20drinking%2C%20bullying%2C%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20criticism%20flared%20again%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20when%20two%20politicians%20from%20different%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20accused%20the%20same%20conservative%20senator%20of%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrews%2C%20who%20will%20retire%20at%20the%20next%20election%2C%20added%20her%20voice%20to%20the%20chorus%20of%20condemnation%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Australian%20broadcaster%20ABC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20did%20have%20one%20of%20my%20male%20colleagues%20who%20used%20to%20breathe%20on%20the%20back%20of%20my%20neck%20in%20question%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrews%20said%20when%20asked%20if%20she%20had%20experienced%20harassment%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20just%20be%20sitting%20there%20minding%20my%20own%20business%20and%20I%20would%20have%20the%20back%20of%20my%20neck%20breathed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20I%20asked%20a%20question%2C%20it%20would%20be%3A%20'That%20was%20a%20great%20question%2C%20thrusting%20and%20probing'...%20that%20sort%20of%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20broad%20review%20published%20in%20November%202021%20found%20that%20one%20in%20three%20people%20working%20inside%20Australia's%20Parliament%20House%20had%20experienced%20some%20form%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20review%2C%20by%20the%20Australian%20Human%20Rights%20Commission%2C%20also%20found%20a%20laddish%20culture%20permeated%20the%20building%2C%20fuelled%20by%20frequent%20bouts%20of%20heavy%20drinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Australia%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of