%20present%20the%20director%20of%20companies%20such%20as%20Larsen%20and%20Toubro%2C%20Hero%20MotoCorp%2C%20Tech%20Mahindra%2C%20CRISIL%20and%20Biocon%20and%20non-executive%20chairman%20of%20IndiGo%2C%20said%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cclearly%20a%20matter%20for%20investigation%20and%20it%20must%20be%20done%20quickly%E2%80%9D.%20He%20added%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20if%20not%20all%20elements%20(of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20story)%20need%20to%20be%20looked%20at.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20is%20based%20on%20documents%20shared%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Report%20Project.%20The%20documents%20were%20also%20given%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20did%20a%20similar%20but%20separate%20story.%20The%20interview%20also%20refers%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20OCCRP%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20specifically%20about%20two%20men%2C%20Nasser%20Ali%20Shaban%20Ahli%20of%20UAE%20and%20Chang%20Chung-Ling%20of%20Taiwan%2C%20who%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%20suggests%20could%20be%20%E2%80%9Cfront%20men%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Adani%20family%2C%20Damodaran%20said%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20possible%20they%20are%20frontmen%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20this%20needs%20to%20be%20examined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDamodaran%20said%20that%20if%2C%20after%20diligent%20examination%2C%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20Ahli%20and%20Chung%20are%20frontmen%2C%20then%20it%20would%20appear%20that%20the%20total%20shareholding%20of%20the%20Adani%20family%20in%20Adani%20Group%20companies%20has%20breached%20SEBI%20regulations.%20In%20that%20event%2C%20he%20said%2C%20one%20legitimate%20suspicion%20would%20be%20the%20possibility%20of%20share%20price%20manipulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhilst%20fulsomely%20praising%20the%20%3Cem%3EFT%3C%2Fem%3E%20story%2C%20Damodaran%20added%20it%20is%20one%20reason%20why%20SEBI%20must%20thoroughly%20investigate%20the%20matter.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20confident%20SEBI%20would%20do%20so%20%E2%80%9Cdiligently%20and%20thoroughly%E2%80%9D%20but%20not%20that%20confident%20of%20how%20quickly%20it%20would%20complete%20the%20investigation.%20As%20Damodaran%20jocularly%20put%20it%2C%20with%20age%20he%20has%20become%20%E2%80%9Cimpatient%E2%80%9D%20and%20wants%20to%20see%20things%20completed%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20the%20interview%20where%20Damodaran%20is%20questioned%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20in%20January%202014%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20had%20raised%20with%20then%20SEBI%20Chairman%2C%20U.%20K.%20Sinha%2C%20fears%20of%20suspicious%20investment%20and%20disinvestment%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group.%20Damodaran%20is%20asked%20if%20SEBI%20took%20this%20seriously.%20Whilst%20the%20DRI%2C%20after%20three%20years%2C%20may%20have%20closed%20its%20own%20investigation%20into%20siphoning%20of%20funds%2C%20the%20fear%20of%20suspicious%20investments%20and%20disinvestments%20in%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20which%20DRI%20sought%20to%20attract%20SEBI%E2%80%99s%20attention%20to%2C%20was%20for%20SEBI%20to%20investigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20light%20of%20the%20conversation%20that%20followed%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20Damodaran%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20an%20apparent%20contradiction%20between%20the%20DRI%20letter%20of%20January%202014%20(when%20Sinha%20was%20chairman%20of%20SEBI)%20and%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5szsK-TcjAc%26ab_channel%3DTheWire%5C%22%3ESinha%20himself%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20an%20interview%20in%20February%202023%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CLet%20me%20say%20that%20to%20the%20best%20of%20my%20information%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20is%20round-tripping%20happening%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20share%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20like%20this%2C%20according%20to%20my%20understanding%20and%20knowledge%2C%20that%20has%20come%20in%20public%20domain%20for%20the%20first%2