22DIPAK%20K%20DASH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A27%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Funion-minister-nitin-gadkari-proposes-10-gst-hike-on-diesel-powered-vehicles%2Farticleshow%2F103598967.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Kashmiris%20Made%20to%20Suffer%20for%20Applause%20from%20Abroad'%3A%20Fears%20Over%20Govt's%20Apple%20Import%20Tariff%20Slash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12115853%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20gaining%20momentum%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20waive%20off%2020%25%20tariff%20on%20imported%20apples%20is%20turning%20into%20a%20fresh%20headache%20for%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%E2%80%99s%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20parties%20in%20Kashmir%20have%20urged%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janta%20Party-led%20Union%20government%20to%20roll%20back%20the%20decision%20while%20local%20stakeholders%20are%20anguished%20that%20the%20waiver%20will%20negatively%20impact%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20apple%20industry%2C%20which%20employs%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20people%20directly%20and%20indirectly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20of%20tariff%2C%20which%20has%20chopped%20off%20extra%2020%25%20from%20the%2070%25%20tariff%20imposed%20since%202019%20by%20New%20Delhi%20on%20the%20premium%20Washington%20apples%2C%20was%20announced%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20state%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20States%20in%20June%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20came%20into%20effect%20on%20September%205%20when%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%20reportedly%20released%20a%20notification%20ahead%20of%20the%20meeting%20between%20Modi%20and%20his%20US%20counterpart%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20G-20%20Summit%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20announced%20the%20tax%20waiver%20on%20several%20US%20products%20such%20as%20walnuts%2C%20lentils%2C%20chickpeas%20and%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fg20-farmers-agriculture-bio-fuel-india-us%5C%22%3EThe%20G20%20Has%20Summarily%20Failed%20to%20Address%20Agrarian%20Distress%20in%20its%20Member%20Countries%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kashmir-based%20traders%20and%20growers%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Washington%20apples%20with%20a%20tax%20waiver%20into%20the%20market%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20set%20to%20pick%20up%20will%20lead%20to%20pricing%20fluctuations%20which%20will%20hit%20the%20local%20industry%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Kashmiris%20put%20in%20agony%20only%20to%20receive%20applause%20from%20foreign%20countries%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHigh%20inflation%20has%20already%20led%20to%20a%20shoot%20up%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20apple%20production%20while%20the%20yield%20has%20also%20fallen%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20tax%20waiver%20%5Bon%20imported%20US%20apples%5D%20will%20hit%20not%20just%20the%20farmers%20of%20Kashmir%20but%20also%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand.%20The%20government%20should%20reconsider%20the%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Bashir%20Ahmad%20Bashir%2C%20president%20of%20the%20All%20Valley%20Fruit%20Growers%20and%20Dealers%20Association%20(AVFGDA)%2C%20the%20leading%20association%20of%20apple%20growers%20and%20traders%20in%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20function%20here%2C%20former%20J%26amp%3BK%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20called%20for%20a%20rollback%20of%20the%20waiver%20while%20alleging%20that%20the%20decision%20%E2%80%9Creflects%20the%20disconnect%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20the%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20directly%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20imported%20apples%2C%20walnuts%20or%20almonds%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hard%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20government%20is%20increasing%20hardships%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Kashmir%20in%20order%20to%20please%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries.%20Kashmiris%20are%20put%20in%20agony%20only%20to%20receive%20applause%20from%20the%20foreign%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERole%20of%20the%20import%20tariff%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmir%20is%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20apple%20basket%2C%20producing%20around%2021%20lakh%20metric%20tonnes%20of%20fruit%20last%20year%20(or%20more%20than%2070%25%20of%20apples%20produced%20in%20India)%20which%20generates%20a%20revenue%20of%20between%20Rs%2010%2C000-Rs%2014%2C000%20crore%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20The%20horticulture%20sector%20contributes%20around%20eight%20to%2010%25%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20India%20and%20the%20US%20were%20caught%20in%20a%20trade%20war%20when%2C%20under%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Washington%20raised%20tariffs%20by%2010-25%25%20on%20specific%20steel%20and%20aluminium%20items%2C%20citing%20national%20security%20concerns.%20India%20followed%20suit%20by%20increasing%20tariffs%20on%20several%20US%20products%2C%20including%20Washington%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20imposition%20of%20extra%20tariff%20drastically%20reduced%20India%E2%80%99s%20apple%20imports%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20From%20US%20%24145.2%20million%20in%202018-19%20when%20the%20country%20imported%20US%20%24305.71%20million%20worth%20of%20apples%20worldwide%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data%2C%20the%20apple%20imports%20dropped%20to%20only%20US%20%245.27%20million%20in%202022-23%20when%20the%20total%20apple%20imports%20were%20at%20US%20%24295.94%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20Turkey%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20leading%20apple%20supplier%20for%20India%2C%20making%20up%20for%20more%20than%2084%25%20of%20total%20apple%20imports%20followed%20by%20Italy%2C%20Chile%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20harvest%20season%20picking%20up%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20premium%20quality%20Washington%20apples%20in%20the%20market%2C%20which%20are%20wax-polished%20to%20increase%20their%20shelf%20life%2C%20has%20dampened%20the%20spirits%20of%20local%20growers%20and%20traders%2C%20who%20were%20hoping%20to%20capitalise%20on%20low%20domestic%20production%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20suffered%20between%2040-50%25%20loss%20of%20apple%20produce%20due%20to%20unseasonal%20rains%2C%20hailstorms%20and%20flood%20which%20led%20to%20spread%20of%20diseases%20such%20as%20scab%20and%20powdery%20mildew%20in%20apple%20trees%20and%20immature%20fruit%20droppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F12172409%2Fapple-himachal-shimla-5503160_1280-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Pexels%2Frohitsinghprashar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Waiver%20will%20narrow%20down%20price%20difference%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20traders%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Red%20Delicious%20variety%2C%20which%20makes%2070-80%25%20of%20total%20apples%20produced%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20sold%20for%20around%20Rs%2075%20per%20kilogram%20in%20the%20wholesale%20market%20last%20year.%20One%20box%20of%20Kashmiri%20Red%20Delicious%20apples%2C%20which%20contains%20around%2020%20kilograms%20of%20fruit%2C%20fetches%20Rs%201%2C200-1%2C500%20in%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Azadpur%20Mandi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20largest%20fruit%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20a%20kilo%20of%20the%20imported%20US%20apples%20sold%20for%20around%20Rs%20120%20in%20the%20wholesale%20market%20of%20Azadpur%20Mandi%2C%20according%20to%20a%20trader.%20A%2032-kg%20box%20sold%20for%20Rs%203%2C000-4%2C000%20last%20year%20while%20a%2025-kg%20box%20fetched%20Rs%202%2C500-3%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revision%20of%20tariff%20will%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20bright-red%20and%20glossy%20Washington%20apples%20in%20wholesale%20markets%20to%20Rs%20100%20a%20kilo%2C%20making%20them%20a%20direct%20and%20more%20powerful%20competitor%20for%20local%20apple%20varieties%20which%20are%20dull%20in%20colour%20and%20also%20lack%20lustre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20waiver%20will%20narrow%20down%20the%20price%20difference%20between%20imported%20and%20local%20apples.%20The%20quality%20of%20imported%20apples%20is%20exceptionally%20high%20and%20our%20apples%20don%E2%80%99t%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20front%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghulam%20Jeelani%20Dar%2C%20an%20apple%20trader%20from%20central%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Ashraf%20Wani%2C%20a%20grower%20from%20Shopian%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20apple%20producing%20districts%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20said%20that%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20US%20are%20more%20advanced%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20use%20of%20farming%20technologies%20and%20the%20subsidies%20provided%20by%20their%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20waiver%20on%20tariff%20will%20hit%20both%20growers%20and%20traders%20in%20India%20equally%20as%20the%20domestic%20varieties%20of%20apples%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20Washington%20apple%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wani%2C%20former%20president%20of%20the%20Shopian%20Fruit%20Mandi%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20traders%20believe%20that%20the%20local%20varieties%20of%20apples%20will%20be%20equally%20in%20high%20demand%20due%20to%20low%20production%20and%20the%20central%20government%E2%80%99s%20waiver%20will%20not%20lower%20the%20prices%20of%20local%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20demand%20for%20apples%20is%20high%20this%20year%20due%20to%20low%20production.%20Thus%20the%20tariff%20waiver%20on%20imported%20apples%20will%20not%20have%20any%20significant%20impact%20on%20local%20producers%20and%20traders%20this%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravinder%20Chauhan%2C%20president%20of%C2%A0%C2%A0Apple%20Growers%20Association%20of%20India%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDuty%20policy%20and%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20imposes%2035%25%20duty%20and%2015%25%20cess%20on%20apple%20imports%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20tariff%20to%2050%25%20of%20cost%2C%20but%20the%20tariff%20was%20set%20at%2070%25%20in%20case%20of%20the%20US%20apples%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%20to%20waive%20off%2020%25%20tariff%20came%20after%20the%20Union%20government%20announced%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20free%20import%20of%20apples%20if%20the%20cost%2C%20insurance%20and%20freight%20(CIF)%20price%20was%20less%20than%20or%20equal%20to%20Rs%2050%20per%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20was%20rolled%20out%20after%20underpriced%20apples%20from%20Iran%20made%20their%20way%20into%20Indian%20markets%20through%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20is%20the%20second%20country%20alongside%20Nepal%20to%20enjoy%20duty-free%20trade%20with%20India%2C%20putting%20the%20local%20growers%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%20on%20the%20back-foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20reports%20of%20many%20growers%20struggling%20to%20recover%20the%20production%20costs%20due%20to%20significantly%20low%20prices%20of%20imported%20apples.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImporting%20apples%20is%20not%20a%20wise%20policy%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wani%2C%20the%20trade%20leader%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20home%20to%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20one-fourth%20population%2C%20our%20country%20is%20sufficient%20to%20consume%20the%20local%20production.%20While%20the%20government%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20increase%20tax%20duty%20to%20avoid%20any%20trade%20issues%20with%20the%20US%2C%20it%20can%20increase%20the%20cess%20on%20imported%20apples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CIf%20Japan%20can%20impose%20100%25%20cess%20on%20rice%20imports%20to%20protect%20local%20farmers%2C%20what%20stops%20the%20Union%20government%20from%20taking%20a%20similar%20decision%3F%20The%20increase%20in%20cess%20will%20provide%20a%20level%20playing%20field%20for%20both%20local%20and%20imported%20apples.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWani%20believes%20that%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20invoke%20CIF%20price%20tag%20on%20imported%20apples%20because%20of%20the%20loss%20of%20tax%20revenue%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20calculated%20decision%20to%20prevent%20tax%20pilferage%20rather%20than%20a%20decision%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers.%20If%20the%20government%20is%20indeed%20concerned%20about%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20apple%20farmers%2C%20it%20should%20announce%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20and%20crop%20insurance%20scheme%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Wani%2C%20the%20grower%20from%20Shopian.%20CIF%20or%20%E2%80%98cost%2C%20insurance%2C%20and%20freight%E2%80%99%20are%20charges%20paid%20by%20a%20seller%20for%20exports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBashir%2C%20the%20AVFGDA%20president%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20should%20impose%20100%25%20import%20duty%20on%20imported%20apples%20if%20it%20wants%20to%20protect%20the%20local%20growers%2C%20%E2%80%9COtherwise%20apple%20farming%20will%20become%20an%20unsustainable%20practice%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeoples%20Democratic%20Party%20President%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20took%20to%20X%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20urging%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Office%20to%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20GOI%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20remove%20additional%20duties%20on%20apples%2C%20walnuts%2C%20and%20almonds%20will%20have%20a%20devastating%20effect%20on%20local%20growers%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20who%20are%20already%20grappling%20with%20huge%20losses%20since%202019.%20I%20hope%20%40PMOIndia%20reconsiders%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694500670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F12115853%2FUntitled-design-3-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fkashmir-apple-import-tariff-reduction%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Kashmir-based%20traders%20and%20growers%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20Washington%20apples%20with%20a%20tax%20waiver%20into%20the%20market%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20apple%20harvest%20season%20is%20set%20to%20pick%20up%20will%20lead%20to%20pricing%20fluctuations%20which%20will%20hit%20the%20local%20industry%20badly.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Fkashmir-apple-import-tariff-reduction%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ST%20Panel%20Seeks%20Action-Taken%20Report%20From%20Manipur%20Govt%20on%20Wrongful%20Hill-Valley%20Demarcation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20124144%2FF1SovOrXoAA5F5U.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(NCST)%20has%20sent%20a%20reminder%20to%20the%20Manipur%20government%20seeking%20an%20action-taken%20report%20on%20its%20recommendations%20made%20in%20a%20December%202022%20report%20which%20flagged%20the%20wrongful%20inclusion%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20hill%20villages%20in%20the%20valley%20districts%2C%20among%20other%20critical%20issues.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20in%20the%20Booklet%20of%20Census%20of%20India%202011%20and%20Administrative%20Atlas%2C%20%E2%80%9CManipur%20has%20wrongly%20included%20several%20hill%20villages%20under%20valley%20districts%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20issue%20had%20been%20flagged%20to%20the%20state%20government%20by%20the%20office%20of%20the%20Registrar%20General%20of%20India%20in%202017%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20revenue%20department%20had%2C%20in%20October%202022%2C%20asked%20the%20deputy%20commissioners%20of%20the%20districts%20concerned%20to%20rectify%20the%20list%20of%20around%20400%20hill%20villages%20overlapping%20between%20the%20districts%20of%20Kakching%2C%20Tengnoupal%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20Bishnupur%2C%20the%20NCST%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20was%20prepared%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Estate%20review%20of%20Manipur%20conducted%20in%20December%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20which%20the%20NCST%20team%20met%20with%20Manipur%20government%20officials%20and%20representatives%20from%20the%20All%20Tribal%20Students%20Union%20Manipur%20(ATSUM)%20and%20the%20Joint%20Coordination%20Committee%20on%20Tribal%20Rights%20in%20Imphal%20(JCCOTR).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20a%20review%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20(AFSPA)%2C%201958%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20hill%20areas%20since%20the%20Act%20had%20been%20withdrawn%20from%2015%20police%20stations%20in%20the%20valley%20districts%2C%20calling%20its%20selective%20implementation%20%E2%80%9Cdiscriminatory%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENCST%20had%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20reserve%20forests%2C%20including%20pocket%20settlements%2C%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20were%20moved%20to%20the%20Imphal%20East%20district%20in%20October%202022%20by%20the%20revenue%20department%20without%20specific%20approval%20from%20the%20Hill%20Areas%20Committee%20(HAC).%20The%20report%20recommended%20that%20this%20order%20should%20be%20reviewed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20its%20representation%2C%20the%20ATSUM%20highlighted%20that%20the%20Meitei%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20ST%20status%20was%20an%20alleged%20attempt%20to%20grab%20tribal%20land.%20It%20noted%20that%20about%20144%20hill%20villages%20had%20been%20placed%20under%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20police%20stations%20in%20valley%20districts%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20name%20of%20convenient%20administration%E2%80%9D%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Csystematic%20way%20of%20encroaching%20into%20hill%20areas%E2%80%9D.%20The%20ATSUM%20had%20also%20added%20that%20several%20hill%20villages%20had%20their%20land%20records%20in%20the%20custody%20of%20adjacent%20valley%20districts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tribal%20bodies%20also%20told%20the%20NCST%20of%20complaints%20about%20the%20majority%20Meitei%2FManipuri%20language%20being%20imposed%20on%20people%20from%20tribal%20communities%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ATSUM%20alleged%20that%20recruitment%20in%20banking%20institutions%20and%20postal%20services%20in%20the%20state%20required%20proof%20of%20passing%20Meitei%2FManipuri%20language%20class%20at%20the%20level%20of%20Class%20X%20or%20XII%2C%20when%20most%20ST%20students%20either%20opt%20for%20English%20or%20their%20traditional%20language%20at%20that%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20commission%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fseveral-hill-villages-in-manipur-wrongly-included-in-valley-districts-st-panel%2Farticle67296353.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520said%2520that%2520in%2520the%2CGeneral%2520of%2520India%2520in%25202017%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20policies%20%E2%80%9Cunfair%20and%20discriminatory%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20report.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694500234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fst-panel-seeks-action-taken-report-in-30-days-from-manipur-govt-on-afspa-border-disputes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20report%20called%20for%20a%20review%20of%20Armed%20Forces%20Special%20Powers%20Act%20(AFSPA)%2C%201958%20in%20hill%20areas%