02.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-1-1694180575-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329488%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJaisimha%20Rao%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20build%20accessible%20and%20reliable%20robots%20for%20long%20term%20and%20sustainable%20farming.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20precision%20agriculture%20a%20reality%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20raised%20in%20Kuwait%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Jaisimha%20completed%20his%20graduation%20in%20electrical%20and%20computer%20engineering%20from%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20USA.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20joined%20a%20company%20in%20New%20York%20and%20worked%20for%20seven%20years%20till%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20in%20my%2020s%2C%20so%20it%20was%20fun%20working%20abroad.%20But%20by%20that%20time%2C%20I%20realised%20how%20my%20future%20in%20the%20corporate%20job%20was%20going%20to%20be%20and%20so%20I%20wanted%20to%20explore%20entrepreneurship%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2037-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20age%20of%2028%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20well-paying%20job%20in%20the%20USA%20and%20came%20back%20to%20his%20family%20to%20settle%20in%20Karnataka.%20While%20his%20peers%20suggested%20he%20explore%20fintech%20entrepreneurship%20given%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20limit%20his%20choices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20when%20he%20went%20to%20a%20coffee%20plantation%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bengaluru%20that%20he%20understood%20his%20purpose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20my%20father%20dragged%20me%20along%20to%20a%20coffee%20plantation%20that%20he%20wished%20to%20purchase.%20While%20conversing%20with%20one%20of%20the%20caretakers%2C%20I%20got%20