em%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Niqo%20Robotics.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694184307000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FNiqo-robotics-1-1694180575.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329484%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jaisimha%20Rao%20innovated%20AI-powered%20spot%20spray%20robots%20which%20selectively%20provide%20cover%20only%20to%20the%20plants%2C%20thereby%20protecting%20the%20soil%20from%20excessive%20chemical%20damage.%20So%20far%2C%20more%20than%20500%20farmers%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%20have%20adopted%20the%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329484%2Fbengaluru-engineer-innovates-artificial-intelligence-powered-robot-sprayers-that-reduce-pesticides-costs-for-farmers%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I-Venture%20%40%20ISB%E2%80%99s%20One-Stop%20Acceleration%20Solution%20Helps%20Women%20Chase%20Their%20Entrepreneurial%20Dreams%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20I-Venture%20%40%20ISB.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI-Venture%20%40%20ISB%E2%80%99s%20I-WIN%20acceleration%20programme%20has%20helped%20several%20women%20entrepreneurs%20scale%20their%20businesses%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20give%20women%20the%20wings%20to%20make%20connections%20in%20the%20business%20world%2C%20but%20also%20helps%20with%20bridging%20several%20existing%20gaps.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20how%20it%20could%20benefit%20you%20too.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Laxmi%20Sri%20Pandrala%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20from%20Bengaluru%20launched%20her%20healthcare%20venture%20Lami.fit%20in%20the%20year%202019%2C%20she%20was%20certain%20it%20was%20a%20step%20to%20revolutionise%20the%20way%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328138%2Fmadurai-dr-swaminathan-doctor-on-wheels-takes-affordable-healthcare-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20was%20perceived%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20Citing%20the%20reasons%20behind%20this%20thought%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20shocking%20revelation%20I%20came%20across%20during%20my%20practice%20is%20that%20one%20in%20four%20Indians%20die%20of%20NCDs%20(non-communicable%20diseases)%2C%20while%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20these%20deaths%20could%20have%20been%20prevented%20were%20the%20condition%20detected%20in%20time.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimple%20changes%20in%20lifestyle%2C%20she%20notes%2C%20could%20bring%20about%20a%20reversal%20of%20the%20condition.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20years%20Laxmi%20spent%20consulting%20at%20a%20hospital%20following%20her%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20nutrition%2C%20she%20came%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20was%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20tackle%20this%20gap%2C%20Laxmi%20started%20her%20venture%20Lami.fit%20based%20upon%20the%20solid%20idea%20that%20good%20health%20was%20within%20reach%20if%20the%20right%20approach%20was%20followed.%20As%20she%20explains%2C%20at%20the%20health%20optimisation%20platform%2C%20a%20full%20workup%20of%20the%20patient%20is%20coupled%20with%20blood%20tests%2C%20followed%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproper%20scientific%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20reports.%20The%20goal%20for%20both%20patient%20and%20doctor%20is%20to%20put%20the%20former%20on%20the%20right%20path.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20she%20says%2C%20will%20encourage%20people%20to%20get%20profess