0ICSE%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ram%20Boojh%2C%20convener%2C%20ICSE%202023%2C%20calls%20the%20conference%20the%20flagship%20programme%20of%20the%20Mobius%20Foundation.%20He%20says%20they%20strongly%20believe%20in%20the%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%2C%20which%20talk%20about%20education%20as%20a%20major%20catalyst%20for%20change%20to%20find%20solutions%20to%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20UN%20SDGs%20are%20the%20basis%20of%20survival%20of%20humanity%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%20It%20guides%20us%20on%20how%20to%20combat%20climate%20change%2C%20create%20better%20health%2C%20access%20affordable%20energy%20and%20fight%20poverty.%20We%20also%20feel%20that%20education%20can%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20transformation%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20intend%20to%20do%20with%20ICSE.%20We%20want%20to%20give%20an%20opportunity%20for%20stakeholders%20and%20students%20to%20come%20together%20to%20encourage%20collective%20action%20and%20share%20ideas%20about%20fighting%20climate%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducation%20as%20a%20tool%20for%20climate%20transformation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%20number%20of%20students%20participated%20in%20ICSE%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-1694094241-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius4-169409424