se%20of%20low%20yields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20perseverance%20paid%20off%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20a%20good%20boost%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290624%2Fmba-graduate-starts-mushroom-farming-during-lockdown-now-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20demand%20for%20oyster%20mushrooms%20in%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20grew.%20This%20also%20motivated%20us%20as%20we%20could%20survive%20at%20a%20time%20when%20others%20were%20losing%20their%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanjay%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20for%20Nidhi%2C%20the%20business%20helped%20her%20feel%20empowered.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20not%20dependent%20on%20any%20private%20institute.%20I%20teach%20for%20my%20passion%20and%20earn%20a%20living%20through%20business.%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20establish%20something%20for%20myself.%20And%20this%20is%20something%20that%20I%20can%20pass%20on%20to%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjournals.innovareacademics.in%2Findex.php%2Fijcpr%2Farticle%2Fview%2F20765%2F11970%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAntidiabetic%20potential%20of%20the%20oyster%20mushroom%20Pleurotus%20Florida%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20By%20Prabu%20M%20and%20Kumuthakalavalli%20R%20published%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Current%20Pharmaceutical%20Research%20in%202017.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Nidhi%20Katare.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694009493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D329202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20college%20where%20she%20taught%20was%20reduced%20to%20ruins%2C%20Professor%20Nidhi%20Katare%20decided%20to%20venture%20into%20entrepreneurship.%20She%20set%20up%20a%20lab%20to%20produce%20mushroom%20spawns%20and%20expanded%20her%20business%20that%20now%20earns%20her%20Rs%201.5%20lakh%20per%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329202%2Fgwalior-professor-nidhi-katare-becomes-successful-mushroom-farmer-earns-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Started%20For%20My%20Daughter%E2%80%99%3A%20Assam%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Vermicompost%20Biz%20Earns%20Her%20Rs%203.5%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202008.%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Kanika%20Talukdar%20was%20abound%20with%20happiness%20as%20her%20daughter%20was%20born%20after%20three%20years%20of%20her%20marriage.%20But%20this%20happiness%20could%20not%20last%20long%20because%20soon%20after%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20husband%20to%20a%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20husband%20was%20down%20with%20a%20fever%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20We%20found%20out%20that%20he%20had%20malaria.%20The%20local%20doctor%20referred%20him%20to%20a%20Guwahati%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20Along%20with%20my%20father%2C%20he%20left%20for%20the%20city%20for%20his%20treatment%2C%20but%20soon%20we%20got%20the%20news%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Borjhar%20village%20resident%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20daughter%20was%20very%20small.%20While%20we%20were%20grieving%20the%20death%20of%20my%20husband%2C%20her%20entire%20future%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20was%20in%20front%20of%20me.%20My%20parents%20brought%20me%20back%20home%20from%20my%20in-laws%E2%80%99.%20I%20thought%20of%20working%20as%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20an%20unwanted%20%3Cem%3Ebojh%20%3C%2Fem%3E(burden)%20for%20my%20elderly%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20encouraged%20Kanika%20to%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%20towards%20self-empowerment.%20Today%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20runs%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249941%2Fhow-to-vermicompost-earn-revenue-sana-khan-sj-organics-earthworms-uttar-pradesh-sustainability-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evermicompost%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20earns%20her%20Rs%203.5%20lakh%20monthly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20just%20Rs%20500%20of%20her%20savings%20and%201%20kg%20of%20earthworms%20provided%20by%20KVK%20in%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20she%20started%20the%20vermicompost%20business.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fkanika-1-1693897088-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-329064%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20just%20Rs%20500%20of%20her%20savings%20and%201%20kg%20of%20earthworms%20provided%20by%20KVK%20in%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20Kanika%20started%20the%20vermicompost%20business.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20She%20Started%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20studied%20till%20class%2012%2C%20Kanika%20struggled%20financially%20and%20professionally.%20To%20fend%20for%20herself%20and%20her%20daughter%2C%20she%20worked%20low-paying%20jobs%20like%20weaving.%20For%20every%20Assamese%20saree%20she%20weaved%2C%20she%20would%20only%20get%20Rs%201%2C000.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20would%20take%20at%20least%20eight%20days%20to%20weave%20a%20saree.%20I%20could%20barely%20earn%20Rs%204%2C000%20in%20a%20month.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20small%20amount%20for%20us%20to%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%202014%20that%20she%20attended%20a%20workshop%20and%20came%20across%20a%20way%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288269%2Ftamil-nadu-home-gardener-starts-business-to-sell-vermicompost-organic-potting-mix-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearn%20better%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20my%20self-help%20group%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20about%20a%20five-day%20workshop%20conducted%20by%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK).%20I%20participated%20in%20it%20and%20got%20to%20know%20about%20several%20business%20opportunities%20like%20fish%20farming%2C%20poultry%2C%20and%20vermicomposting.%20I%20got%20very%20interested%20in%20vermicomposting%20as%20I%20had%20easy%20access%20to%20all%20the%20raw%20materials%20like%20cow%20dung%20and%20leaves%20at%20my%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%20in%20all%20these%20years%2C%20Kanika%20felt%20optimistic.%20With%20just%20Rs%20500%20of%20her%20savings%20and%201%20kg%20of%20earthworms%20provided%20by%20KVK%20in%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20she%20started%20the%20vermicompost%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%2