E2%80%9D%20reminisces%20Anuradha%20Budhraja%2C%20when%20speaking%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELong-standing%20dream%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Himalayas%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20us%20living%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20overlooking%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311053%2Fdushyant-vashisht-turned-cottage-to-sustainable-homestay-bir-terraces-uttarakhand-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHimalayan%20ranges%20with%20nature%20around%20us%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20our%20dream.%20This%20dream%20became%20more%20urgent%20when%20we%20visited%20Thanedar%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20in%202005%20to%20attend%20a%20local%20%3Cem%3Emela%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fair)%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Anuradha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-1-1693576300.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20library%20in%20the%20house%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-1-1693576300.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-1-1693576300-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-1-1693576300-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-1-1693576300-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-1-1693576300-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnuradha%20and%20Kartik%20moved%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Himachal%20as%20they%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20do%20something%20of%20their%20own%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Kartik%20Budhraja%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20place%20and%20wanted%20to%20move%20there.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20Anuradha%20and%20Kartik%20were%20working%20as%20media%20professionals%20in%20Singapore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20urge%20to%20come%20back%20to%20India%20was%20mainly%20for%20two%20reasons.%20Firstly%2C%20we%20both%20wanted%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20rat%20race%20and%20build%20a%20business%20of%20our%20own%2C%20and%20secondly%2C%20we%20loved%20the%20mountains%20and%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20few%20years%20of%20planning%20and%20iterating%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20finally%20make%20the%20move.%20We%20quit%20our%20jobs%20and%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20moved%20to%20Thanedar%20and%20started%20a%20fruit%20jam%20business%20utilising%20the%20fruits%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20setting%20up%20the%20factory%20and%20settling%20ourselves%20in%20the%20environment%2C%20we%20really%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20permanent%20home.%20By%202017%2C%20we%20were%20actively%20looking%20for%20a%20suitable%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Kartik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%20in%202017%2C%20at%20the%20same%20annual%20%3Cem%3Emela%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Thanedar%2C%20the%20couple%20found%20their%20dream%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20girls%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20of%20our%20jams%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emela%3C%2Fem%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20farmers%20from%20Saroga%20village%20came%20up%20to%20us%20and%20asked%20why%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20cherry%20jams.%20Jokingly%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98if%20we%20come%20to%20his%20village%20he%20would%20give%20us%20cherries%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Anuradha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20response%2C%20I%20said%20that%20we%20will%20buy%20cherries%20only%20if%20he%20gets%20us%20a%20house%20in%20his%20village.%20All%20we%20know%20is%20that%20the%20next%20day%2C%20we%20are%20driving%20up%20to%20the%20village%2C%20meeting%20the%20same%20farmer%20again%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20land%20that%20was%20to%20become%20our%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Anuradha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pictures%20of%20the%20house%20when%20covered%20in%20snow%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328889%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20house%20has%20a%20rainwater%20harvesting%20system%20and%20solar%20panels%20to%20provide%20electricity%20to%20the%20house%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Kartik%20Budhraja%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribing%20the%20land%2C%20Kartik%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20everything%20we%20had%20dreamt%20of.%20It%20stood%208000%20sq%20ft%20above%20sea%20level%20with%20an%20amazing%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20Satluj%20River%20on%20the%20other.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20decided%20to%20purchase%20the%20land%20and%20hence%20began%20the%20journey%20of%20making%20their%20dream%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Waking%20up%20to%20the%20Himalayas%20in%20our%20nature-friendly%20home%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20land%20was%20only%20six%20kilometres%20from%20our%20factory%20and%20on%20three%20elevations.%20We%20decided%20not%20to%20touch%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20it%20and%20instead%20build%20our%20home%20around%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilt%20on%20three%20levels%2C%20the%20house%20has%20three%20bedrooms%2C%20three%20bathrooms%2C%20one%20parlour%20room%20and%20a%20living%20room.%20Along%20with%20a%20dining%20room%20and%20a%20kitchen%2C%20it%20also%20has%20a%20pantry%2C%20a%20gym%2C%20a%20library%20and%20a%20lounge.%20The%20house%20has%20its%20own%20storeroom%2C%20an%20attic%2C%20and%20quarters%20for%20domestic%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20shape%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20land%20and%20decided%20to%20not%20level%20it.%20The%20house%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20it%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20does%20not%20look%20like%20an%20eyesore%20on%20the%20beautiful%20hill.%20Instead%2C%20it%20blends%20with%20nature%20and%20actually%20looks%20like%20a%20part%20of%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20philosophy%20of%20the%20couple%20behind%20building%20the%20house%20was%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20it%20to%20be%20efficient%2C%20cosy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187566%2Fchennai-architect-sustainable-homes-eco-friendly-construction-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20nature-friendly.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20the%20sole%20designers%20