n%20vegetables%20such%20as%20spinach%2C%20white%20pigweed%2C%20herbs%20such%20as%20parsley%20and%20wild%20mint%20and%20a%20few%20local%20varieties%20of%20kidney%20beans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Inspiring%20locals%20to%20follow%20nature-friendly%20living%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20couple%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20making%20the%20house%20their%20dream%20home%2C%20they%20also%20wanted%20to%20spread%20a%20strong%20message.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20many%20ways%20one%20can%20live%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature%2C%20it%20is%20all%20about%20going%20the%20extra%20mile.%20Especially%20with%20nature%2C%20we%20need%20to%20be%20more%20careful%20with%20the%20nature%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20opines%20Anuradha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStraight%20buildings%20which%20are%20front%20heavy%20and%20rectangular%20put%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20the%20land%20which%20then%20results%20in%20landslides.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20have%20made%20the%20house%20into%20three%20levels%20so%20that%20we%20did%20not%20have%20to%20do%20any%20cutting%20of%20the%20land%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kartik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20almost%20felt%20selfish%20to%20have%20so%20much%20and%20not%20share%20it%20with%20others.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20in%202022%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20host%20a%20few%20guests%20and%20share%20this%20beauty%20with%20others%20too.%20We%20started%20to%20host%20a%20B%26amp%3BB%20under%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Saroga%20Woods%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anuradha%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20B%26amp%3BB%2C%20guests%20have%20the%20chance%20to%20explore%20the%20local%20village%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312314%2Fthinles-singhey-starts-jimpo-a-sea-buckthorn-brand-in-ladakh-fruit-berry-jam-juice-squash%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenjoy%20jam-making%20%3C%2